g a Peltier element\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"but it\'s still a problem\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(11,27,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Savant syndrome?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Am I sick?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I didn\'t say it\'s about you, Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Only that there are people who suffer from that sickness.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"If it\'s not about me\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"then why are talking about it?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"There are other children who may learn from your example.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I\'m only myself.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Not other children.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"That\'s true!\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I\'m sorry, Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"What\'s wrong, Lain?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"Why are you calling me Lain?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"Who are you?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(12,31,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"When we are not connected to the network\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"we are all alone.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Do you understand that?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(13,33,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Stop it!\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"You have to be still!\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(14,34,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Dont do that. You have to stay calm... It finally came.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"...\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Lain, concerning your inquiry, I think your approach is the correct one.\", \"actor\": \"Computer\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"...\", \"actor\": \"Computer\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"The concept of a neural network is a relatively old idea, but the arrangement of neurons by any system may not necessarily make the system work...\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"It wont work.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Ha, ha.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(15,35,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"But even if it is assumed to be complete, there will definitely be an unknown network that connects people.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"It might be one of many things, like Jungs ideas of the subconscious.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"There are many ways to say it, but no one can prove its existence now...\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"But thinking about a person like you who has an interest in this sort of thing, I wonder, what are you trying to research?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"What is your goal?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(16,37,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Wave interference.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(17,38,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I don\'t believe it\'s you.\", \"actor\": \"Guy\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"How old are you?\", \"actor\": \"Guy\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Oh, I\'m sorry.\", \"actor\": \"Guy\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"You shouldn\'t ask women about their age.\", \"actor\": \"Guy\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I don\'t normally get a chance to talk with girls your age.\", \"actor\": \"Guy\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"And to be honest, it\'s making me a bit nervous.\", \"actor\": \"Guy\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Do you have what you promised?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"The actuator motor.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"It\'s a rare thing.\", \"actor\": \"Guy\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Watch out for electricity.\", \"actor\": \"Guy\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"No worries.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"So sure?\", \"actor\": \"Guy\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"What are you building anyway?\", \"actor\": \"Guy\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"Myself.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"And something that gave me a body.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"But it\'s only temporary.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"So there\'s no point in developing it.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"I don\'t think I quite understand\", \"actor\": \"Guy\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"Things are born when you build them.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"And when they are destroyed, they transform into something else.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"Something completely new.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 21, \"text\": \"Do you know what\'s going on?\", \"actor\": \"Guy\"}]'),(18,42,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Stop!\", \"actor\": \"Guy\"}]'),(19,44,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Lain?\", \"actor\": \"Guy\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Lain!\", \"actor\": \"Guy\"}]'),(20,45,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"What\'s going on?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}]'),(21,46,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Lain!\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"When you appeared in a laboratory two years ago\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"all data about you was entered into a database.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"You know that.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Archives of movies recorded by your family.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"The contents of your personal computer.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"We had it all in data.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"But there\'s something strange\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"The last data update\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}]'),(22,47,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"is about your future!\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"It\'s a record from a day two years in the future!\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Who are you?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Talk to me!\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Why isn\'t there any data prior to three years ago?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"No!\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"You were born in your current form\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"It doesn\'t matter in this world.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"You know that.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Stay away!\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I want to connect with the entire world.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(23,50,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Guy\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"You\", \"actor\": \"Guy\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I finished.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"What are you talking about?\", \"actor\": \"Guy\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"About my dad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"What?\", \"actor\": \"Guy\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Lain!\", \"actor\": \"Guy\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Lain!\", \"actor\": \"Guy\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Lain?\", \"actor\": \"Guy\"}]'),(24,54,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"It\'s over.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"For me it\'s the beginning.\", \"actor\": \"Lain2\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"From now on we will always be together.\", \"actor\": \"Lain2\"}]'),(25,57,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"So Mrs. Iwakura, please wait here in the antechamber.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Lain, you dont have to worry so much.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Please sit down there.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Ah do you want some juice or something else to drink?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Its OK if you dont worry so much.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Let\'s see.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I\'m thirsty, so I\'m going for tea mind to follow me?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Because it will look funny if only I drink it.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Thank you.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Which one should it be?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"We have many to choose from.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"The same as you.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"Green tea?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"Got it.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"Just a moment\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"You put in the sugar and milk by yourself, OK?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"Here you go.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"So where should we start?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"How is this? Earl Grey tea, I really love it.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"Earl Grey?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"Right.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 21, \"text\": \"Even with tea there are lots of kinds, with different smell and taste.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 22, \"text\": \"Does it taste good?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 23, \"text\": \"Yes.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 24, \"text\": \"It suits my taste.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 25, \"text\": \"But I\'m not sure about you Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 26, \"text\": \"If you want to, you can drink a little bit.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 27, \"text\": \"If its not to your taste, I can make something else for you.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 28, \"text\": \"Here\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}]'),(26,58,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"That smells good.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Here you go.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"How is it?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Looks as if you dont like it, huh?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Too bitter?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"What if you add some sugar?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Well, how about if you add some milk?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"It might take away the bitterness.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Or I can get you something else?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"I dont like milk.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Ah, sorry. I didnt know... Well, how about if I get some juice for you?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Im sorry...\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"Thats all right; I probably couldnt have had green tea either at your age.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"You said that there are lots of different kinds of tea right?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"If I dont like it, I dont like it.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"Of course, that doesnt mean I cant drink it, but different kinds of tea have different flavors right?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"What do you like, Lain?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"Why dont you like milk?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"It upsets my stomach.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"Ha, ha, truth be told, when I was a child I had the same problem.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"Especially when the school lunch included milk, I can drink milk now though.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 21, \"text\": \"I cant drink it, but I really love it...\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 22, \"text\": \"How about milk that doesnt upset your stomach? Would that be all right?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 23, \"text\": \"Whats it called?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 24, \"text\": \"I forgot what its called, but its milk that doesnt upset your stomach.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 25, \"text\": \"I have it for kids like you Lain, who are like me as a kid and cant drink milk.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 26, \"text\": \"If you talk about it with your mother, Im sure shell look for it for you.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}]'),(27,59,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Are there different kinds of milk as well?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Thats right; although theyre basically all they same, depending on how theyre prepared there are different kinds.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Different kinds?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Yes, in tea too.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Depending on the way the leaves are dried and the way the tea is poured, the same leaves can be very different.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"People too?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Hmm?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Are there different kinds of people as well?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Hmm, well, rather than kinds, each person is different in his or her own way.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"For example, you dont like tea, but there are also people like me who love it.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"There are also people whose stomach gets upset when they drink milk, but there also those whose stomach doesnt get upset right?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"However, there also people who when they grow up, learn to drink it.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"Lain, youll probably will learn to drink tea you know.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"Its not a good thing, nor a bad thing.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"Its normal that there are different kinds of people.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"Thats why you can just ignore rather you should be proud of your uniqueness I think!\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"Be proud of it?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"Im sorry... Thats right, you worry, dont you?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"You dont have to boast about it, but theres no need to mind what other people think is what I meant to say.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"I have weird dreams, is that different too?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"You may think its different, but in fact thats normal.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 21, \"text\": \"If youre worried about that, I might be able to help.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 22, \"text\": \"Not to help you stop having those dreams, but rather helping you to explain things you dont understand.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 23, \"text\": \"If you come to me with your problems, Id be really happy.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 24, \"text\": \"You know, Ive studied a lot to help you answer those kinds of questions; Im still studying actually.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 25, \"text\": \"If youre ever in trouble or something, and should you want to come and talk to me, thatd be OK. Id like to know more about you Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 26, \"text\": \"Would that be OK?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 27, \"text\": \"Im so glad!\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 28, \"text\": \"Starting today you and I are friends!\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 29, \"text\": \"Please come and play sometime!\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 30, \"text\": \"Promise?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 31, \"text\": \"Id like to ask you things as well!\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 32, \"text\": \"You can ask me anything you want.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 33, \"text\": \"If I dont know the answer Ill look up the answer for you.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 34, \"text\": \"Ill even prepare your favorite drink.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 35, \"text\": \"Whats that??\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 36, \"text\": \"Milk that doesnt upset your stomach!\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}]'),(28,60,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"7th of July, 2pm, 2nd session\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Come on in.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Touko, Touko, hello.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Hello, Lain\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Hello.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Its almost the summer holidays! Are you looking forward to them?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Not especially.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Lets see here, today, today Id like to play a game with you Lain, thats why I brought this.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Whats that?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Its oil painting set. Do you like picture Lain?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I dont like paintings... Maybe...\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"I see Well, do you know tic-tac-toe?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"I know it, but I dont want to play that\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"I Im sorry. Im a bit frazzled today. Well, do you have anything you want to do Lain?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"Id like to talk some more\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"What do you want to talk about?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"Whatever. About you.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"About me? Well Im not that interesting you know.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"Yes, you are.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"No really, Im not that interesting.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"But look, Im already 27, if we talked about me wed have to start all the way at the beginning and itd take forever!\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 21, \"text\": \"And really, its not a very interesting story at that.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 22, \"text\": \"What kind of doctor are you?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 23, \"text\": \"What kind of doctor you ask?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 24, \"text\": \"Well, I help people like you who worry about certain things, and listen to their stories.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 25, \"text\": \"And I give them advice to help fix their problems.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 26, \"text\": \"You understand?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 27, \"text\": \"Ah I thought so\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 28, \"text\": \"Whats wrong?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 29, \"text\": \"If youre not feeling well, or youre not comfortable please tell me, you can be honest with me.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 30, \"text\": \"I should be more careful really.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 31, \"text\": \"You shouldnt worry so much.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 32, \"text\": \"Just relax, come and have a nice talk with me once a month.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 33, \"text\": \"Okay\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(29,61,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"So, hows school?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Normal.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"By normal you mean? Not interesting, not boring, just normal?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Yes\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"How about friends?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I have friends.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Do you often play with them?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Yes, but everyones busy with cram school. The only place I go is here\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Dont you want to learn something? Calligraphy, or take swimming lesso ooohhh\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Its ok; dont worry about it.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Im sorry\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Id rather stay at home than go out and do something.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"What do you do at home?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"Thats a secret.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"Aw, thats mean. You wont tell me.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"But Im ashamed.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"Are you doing things youre ashamed of?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"Maybe\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"Now I want to know! Ah, so be it But Id really like to know\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"If I dont tell you is that bad?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"Id be glad if you did tell me.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 21, \"text\": \"I talk to my stuffed animals.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 22, \"text\": \"Ha, ha, is that it? Thats completely normal. I knew it.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 23, \"text\": \"Knew what?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 24, \"text\": \"Ha, ha, never mind! I used to have a stuffed animal I loved\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 25, \"text\": \"What kind of stuffed animal?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 26, \"text\": \"A dragon I got at the bank. Weird huh?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 27, \"text\": \"Why is that weird?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 28, \"text\": \"Well, arent girls supposed to play with cute stuffed animals?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 29, \"text\": \"It wasnt even a stuffed animal it was a piggy bank dragon.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 30, \"text\": \"But I still treasured it.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 31, \"text\": \"I called it Ta-chan and talked to it all the time.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 32, \"text\": \"Me too. I talk to my animals. Is that normal?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 33, \"text\": \"Thats normal! Do I look weird to you??\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 34, \"text\": \"No\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 35, \"text\": \"Youre the same as me, Lain, were not weird at all!\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}]'),(30,62,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Hello Lain, have you been well?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Yes, and you?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Yes, Ive been fine. Im a bit tired though.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Tired?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Yes, Ive been pretty busy.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"With what?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Hmm, well... At least talking with you like this is something I can look forward to.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Really?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Really! What shall we talk about today What do you want to talk about Lain?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"I want to talk about you, doctor. We werent able to last month.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Id rather talk about you, Lain; not about myself, though.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"But youre right, its only fair that we both get to talk about what we want, so this time well talk about me, but next time well talk about you Lain, is that all right?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"OK!\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"Im not sure where I should start though... My name is Younera Touko, Im 27, Im a doctor at the Tokyo Research Institute for Psychotherapy Thats this place.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"Ah, we wont get anywhere like this.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"You know, Im used to listening people talk, not used to talking myself.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"Is there anything youd like to know Lain?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"How did you become a doctor?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"I studied a lot at a place called a university.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"I wrote something called a thesis, and with that I received my degree to become a doctor.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}]'),(31,63,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"What is college like?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Youre in junior high school now arent you, Lain?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"So if youre in junior high and want to keep studying, you go to high school, right?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"College is where people go if they want to keep studying after high school.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Do you like to study, Sensei?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I didnt used to.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"But I went to America as an exchange student when I was in junior high school, and I started to feel differently then.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"You were an exchange student. Wow!\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"At the time, I just went because my parents wanted me to.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"But people have different ways of seeing things in other countries, and I learned a lot from that.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Looking back, it was a lot of work, and at first, I didn\'t feel good about it, but now Im really grateful that I was able to be an exchange student.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"I learned English, too.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"Thats amazing, Toko Sensei!\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"Oh, its not so amazing.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"There are lots of people who have studied much more than I have.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"Im really a pretty lazy person.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"I liked to fool around, really.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"Its boring to just study, isnt it?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"Do you like to study, Lain?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"Not really.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"What subjects dont you like?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 21, \"text\": \"Japanese and physical education.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 22, \"text\": \"I see. So you dont like exercise.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 23, \"text\": \"No, I dont like physical education.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 24, \"text\": \"You like exercise, then?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 25, \"text\": \"Yes.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 26, \"text\": \"What kind of exercise do you like?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 27, \"text\": \"The metal beam.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 28, \"text\": \"Wow!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 29, \"text\": \"I used to like running, but I was never good at the metal beam.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 30, \"text\": \"I would spin around and get too dizzy.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 31, \"text\": \"I like to spin around.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 32, \"text\": \"Both frontwards and backwards?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 33, \"text\": \"Yes, both.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 34, \"text\": \"What dont you like?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 35, \"text\": \"(silence)\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 36, \"text\": \"You dont have to answer if you dont want to.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 37, \"text\": \"But, what kind of study do you like?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 38, \"text\": \"I\'m sorry.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 39, \"text\": \"Are you tired?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 40, \"text\": \"Why don\'t we end early today?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(32,64,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Im sorry about last time but Im relieved.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I was worried that you didnt like me and wouldn\'t come anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Im sorry.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Theres no reason to apologize.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I was the one who asked you a bad question.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Can you forgive me?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"thank you.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"So I thought we could work with this today. Can we talk about this?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"They had that at the last hospital.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Really? I wanted to play with this.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"What kind of test is it?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Amazing Lain! Do you know about it?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"They call this a Rorschach Test.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"This isnt really a test.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"Think of it as a game.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"But thats boring.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"Hmm I guess so.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"If you think it\'s boring, we\'ll stop the test.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"Hows that?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"Okay.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"Okay. What do you see?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 21, \"text\": \"A splotch.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 22, \"text\": \"Um, right.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 23, \"text\": \"But does it look like anything?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 24, \"text\": \"What do you see?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 25, \"text\": \"Me? Hmm a persons face, I think.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 26, \"text\": \"Is it angry? Is it also crying?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 27, \"text\": \"It looks a little angry.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 28, \"text\": \"This is boring.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 29, \"text\": \"Lain\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 30, \"text\": \"Right. A promise is a promise. Lets stop.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}]'),(33,65,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Do you want to talk about something fun? Do you like to take a bath or a shower?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I like showers.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Really?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I prefer baths, but I dont get a chance to take them much at home.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Its a bit of a hassle to prepare for a bath, too.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I usually take showers, but I take a bath on my days off.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Dont you like the way a bath feels?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Im afraid of being in hot water.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"You don\'t like to get wet?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"No.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Then, what are you afraid of?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Im not really sure. It feels like Im being touched all over by something.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"Hmm the water does touch the skin.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(34,66,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Its because Im weird\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Wait a second Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Youre not a weird kid at all.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Everyone thinks theyre weird when theyre kids...\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"But youre wrong.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Do you dislike being different from others?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Im not sure.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Okay?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Lain is Lain because she is different.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"You have a very strong imagination, and thats a good thing.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"So dont say that you\'re weird.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"I dont think that at all.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"But the test\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"Im sorry but youre troubled, right?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"I want you to not to be troubled.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"In order to help you, I have to know more about you.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"I dont want to make you uncomfortable.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"What should I do?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"Right now you don\'t need to do anything.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"Since you and I are friends, if we keep talking, Ill slowly start to understand more and more about you.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"So, if I say, I think you should come over, it would be good for you to think, That sounds nice, okay....\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 21, \"text\": \"So right now, itd be best if you tell me all about yourself.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 22, \"text\": \"You wont tell anyone?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 23, \"text\": \"Nope, itll be our secret.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 24, \"text\": \"Not even your friends, or your mother?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 25, \"text\": \"I promise. If I lie, one thousand needles!\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 26, \"text\": \"One thousand needles?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 27, \"text\": \"Dont kids your age know that?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 28, \"text\": \"When I was a kid, whenever we made a promise, we said, If I break the promise, I will drink 1000 needles.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 29, \"text\": \"Wouldnt that hurt?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 30, \"text\": \"A lot!!... Right! How many needles are in my stomach right now? Miss Iwakura?...\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 31, \"text\": \" five thousand?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 32, \"text\": \"Wrong! Yesterday, since I went to the bathroom and flushed everything out, theres zero!\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 33, \"text\": \"Sensei, that\'s gross!...\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(35,67,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Hello, Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"(in a soft voice) Hello.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Hmm.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"You dont sound so energetic.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Maybe you dont feel up for this.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Why dont we quit now?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Ok?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"But since you came all the way out here, how would you like a cup of tea or something?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"What would you like?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Dont be shy.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I want to talk.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"You dont have to force yourself. That might make you feel even worse. Take my word for it.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"I want to be cured.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"Curedbut youre not sick, Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"But this is a hospital isnt it?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"Well, this place can function as a hospital, but I see patients at my research room as well.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"Right now, I dont know if you are really sick or not.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"My hunch is that you are probably not sick, Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"Still, if you arent feeling well or are worried about something, Id like to be able to help you.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"Im not sick?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"Right now, Im not completely sure, but youre probably just fine.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 21, \"text\": \"Even if you are sick, Ill make sure that you are cured.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 22, \"text\": \"Youre absolutely sure you can cure me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 23, \"text\": \"Absolutely. I will not let you be sick.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 24, \"text\": \"Sensei, why are you so kind to me? Is it because it is your job?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 25, \"text\": \"Hmm Youre right that this is a part of my work.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 26, \"text\": \"But its a type of work thats hard to see as just work.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 27, \"text\": \"Most of the time, I see patients, diagnose them as objectively as possible, and give them psychological treatment, but it isnt enough to make them better.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 28, \"text\": \"Im a researcher as well as a doctor.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 29, \"text\": \"If I see someone suffering, I must try and help that person.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 30, \"text\": \"I want to do everything I can to help that person.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 31, \"text\": \"You would do that for anybody?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 32, \"text\": \"To be specific, if I see someone suffering from something for which the cause is physical and obvious, I refer that person to a specialist.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 33, \"text\": \"If there is a car accident or a poisoning, that\'s what I would do.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 34, \"text\": \"Do put it simply, Im not the kind of doctor who treats people who have something wrong with them physically.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 35, \"text\": \"So I have\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 36, \"text\": \"I cant tell for sure without doing a close examination, but I know that you had an examination before you came here and that no problems were found.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 37, \"text\": \"And just by talking to you here, Lain, you dont seem to have anything wrong with you at all.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 38, \"text\": \"But I have to have you talk to me and tell me much more about whats going on with you I cant really help you with whats bothering you.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(36,68,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"What bothers me is that I have nightmares, I see strange things, I feel that someone is touching me when no one is there.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I have symptoms of schizophrenia.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Schizophrenia? Where did you hear a word like that? Who said that to you?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I looked it up in a book.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Lain, its a good things to study hard, but its dangerous to go digging around and diagnosing yourself when you arent sick.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Have you heard the expression a lot of how sick you feel depends on what you think about it?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Actually I havent.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Oh?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Anyway, if you start diagnosing yourself, youre going to start believing that you have all sorts of things wrong with you.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"But I wanted to know whats wrong with me. I wanted to understand.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I see.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"I understand.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"I think youre intentions are right.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"But Id like to ask something of you.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"Please dont go around imagining and concocting searching, for things that you think are wrong with you.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"Can I ask that of you?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"Then will you help me find whats wrong?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"Of course I will.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"So lets make a promise.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"I will tell you everything I understand about you.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"I wont hide anything from you.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 21, \"text\": \"If you lie can I cut off your finger?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 22, \"text\": \"Hmm you can do something even worse. You can hammer a nail into my head.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 23, \"text\": \"Youre goofy, Sensei.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 24, \"text\": \"Seriously, though, I really want to help you.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 25, \"text\": \"Im an only child, and I always wished I had a younger sistersomeone like you, Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 26, \"text\": \"Youre my big sister then?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 27, \"text\": \"Id be happy if you saw it that way.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 28, \"text\": \"I will.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 29, \"text\": \"Thank you. Anyway, lets end for today. Youre tired arent you?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 30, \"text\": \"Uh, uh. But Ill do what you asked me to do, Sensei.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 31, \"text\": \"Great! Hee, hee. Actually, Im the one whos tired.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 32, \"text\": \"Youre tired of me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 33, \"text\": \"No, no!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 34, \"text\": \"Dont think that.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 35, \"text\": \"Ive had a lot of other work to do today, too.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 36, \"text\": \"I like you and Ill miss you until we meet again, Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 37, \"text\": \"That makes me feel better.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 38, \"text\": \"Lets end now, then. Its getting late and we dont want your mother to worry.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 39, \"text\": \"Goodbye, Toko Sensei.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 40, \"text\": \"Goodbye, Lain-chan.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 41, \"text\": \"Just call me Lain. Its a bit weird for a big sister to call me Lain-chan.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 42, \"text\": \"Ok then, goodbye, Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 43, \"text\": \"Goodbye.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(37,69,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Hello, Toko-san.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Hello, Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Ok, from today were going to really tackle whats bothering you, Lain-chan.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Im sorry.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I mean Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Were going to try to figure things out so you dont see nightmares anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Uh, huh. I havent seen nightmares much lately, though. Sometimes I hear things, though.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Hear things? Like what?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I dont know.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"It sounds like someone talking.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I dont like hearing it, so I try my best to ignore it.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Hmm. Do you know whose voice you hear?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"I dont know. It can be a mans voice or a womans voice.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"Where do the voices seem to come from?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"From the sky.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"The sky? From what part of the sky?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"From the electric lines. Somehow\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"The electric lines Do you know whats in side of electric lines?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"Wiring that carries electricity.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"Right. They carry electricity that comes from power plants. Do feel like you sense electricity?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"I don\'t really know. Sometimes it seems to come from the sky; not the electric lines.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 21, \"text\": \"Are you bothered by it right now?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 22, \"text\": \"No. Im not scared now. But\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 23, \"text\": \"When you told your mother, did she tell you not to tell anyone else about these things?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 24, \"text\": \"Uh huh.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 25, \"text\": \"People who dont hear these things would think strange things about you if you told them, huh?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 26, \"text\": \"You dont have to worry about telling me anything you want to.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 27, \"text\": \"You dont have to worry.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 28, \"text\": \"Ok?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 29, \"text\": \"Im not going to think strange things about you.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 30, \"text\": \"Because Im sick?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 31, \"text\": \"No, Lain. Lets see. You know about kanashibari?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 32, \"text\": \"When a ghost comes out and you cant move your body?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 33, \"text\": \"Right. Have you ever had that happen to you?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 34, \"text\": \"Many times.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 35, \"text\": \"It was frightening, wasnt it?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 36, \"text\": \"Uh, huh.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 37, \"text\": \"Do you know why kanashibari happens?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 38, \"text\": \"Why?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 39, \"text\": \"The human body is very mysterious.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 40, \"text\": \"When youre sleeping, there are times when your mind is awake, times when your body is awake.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 41, \"text\": \"Do you understand?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 42, \"text\": \"Sort of\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 43, \"text\": \"Well, thats good enough for now. What parts of you are awake right now?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 44, \"text\": \"My body and my mind.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 45, \"text\": \"Hmm.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 46, \"text\": \"Suppose I said something really scary right now and you feel scared enough to run out of this room.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 47, \"text\": \"What would you do?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 48, \"text\": \"I think I would run out of this room.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 49, \"text\": \"Ok.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 50, \"text\": \"Suppose that you feel so scared that you want to run out of this room, but your body is asleep and you cant move.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 51, \"text\": \"Thats what kanashibari is.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 52, \"text\": \"So if youre having a nightmare but your body is asleep and you cant move, you are having kanashibari.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 53, \"text\": \"You see?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 54, \"text\": \"If you know whats involved, its not so scary, is it?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 55, \"text\": \"No. It isnt.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(38,70,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"There are many people who have had experienced kanashibari, but we dont call them sick.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"But\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Hmm there might be only a few people who have experienced what you have.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Still, I dont think you should be called sick just because of your experiences.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"A lot of things can happen to a person while shes young and impressionable.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"But Im scared and I hate this.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"What are the scariest parts of your dreams?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I start to feel that I dont need myself. I feel that I am an unneeded thing.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"You dont need yourself?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"I feel that I am being told to come back because Im unneeded.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Come back? Come back where?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"To myself.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"Hmm. This is hard to understand. You want you to come back to yourself?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"I dont know. But for a person like me to be me, and to touch body, feels like Im being torn\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"(interrupting) And its painful?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"It isnt painful, but its frightening.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"I see. Does this happen when youre asleep?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"Probably.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"Probably? This happens sometimes when youre not dreaming?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"I don\'t know.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"Sometimes it happens when Im just sitting by myself, and sometimes when Im talking to my friends.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 21, \"text\": \"Tell me what happens when youre not alone. This happens when youre just having conversations?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 22, \"text\": \"Yes. While Im just talking, it suddenly\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 23, \"text\": \"How do you notice it? Do your friends call out to you?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 24, \"text\": \"Suddenly\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 25, \"text\": \"Is there something that triggers it?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 26, \"text\": \"I was afraid, and I felt better after staying motionless for a while.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 27, \"text\": \"Can you explain what it felt like, or what you saw? Could you draw a picture?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 28, \"text\": \"No, I cant.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 29, \"text\": \"I see Oh!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 30, \"text\": \"We have to end.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 31, \"text\": \"Im sorry, Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 32, \"text\": \"I have to go out and take care of some things today.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 33, \"text\": \"Im sorry to have to stop right in the middle of our appointment.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 34, \"text\": \"But its good for now that you cant see these things.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 35, \"text\": \"I think that what you experience probably has something to do with kanashibari.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 36, \"text\": \"Ill do some research on it until next month.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 37, \"text\": \"Thatll be my homework.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 38, \"text\": \"Your homework will be keeping a diary.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 39, \"text\": \"A diary?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 40, \"text\": \"I want you to write about the things you did during the day, and what you thought about.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 41, \"text\": \"You dont have to show it to me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 42, \"text\": \"Just write what you want.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 43, \"text\": \"I used to keep a diary when I was your age.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 44, \"text\": \"But\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 45, \"text\": \"You don\'t want to?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 46, \"text\": \"It can be really interesting to look back on the things you write in your diary.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 47, \"text\": \"We can be forgetful, so it can help you remember things, too.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 48, \"text\": \"That will cure me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 49, \"text\": \"Hmm.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 50, \"text\": \"That probably doesnt have anything to do with it.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 51, \"text\": \"It cant hurt, though.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 52, \"text\": \"Ill explain more carefully next month.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 53, \"text\": \"I dont mind if you dont want to keep a diary.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 54, \"text\": \"I went and bought you a diary book, though.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 55, \"text\": \"See?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 56, \"text\": \"Its cute, isnt it?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 57, \"text\": \"I found it when I went shopping last week, and I thought it would be a nice present for you.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 58, \"text\": \"Thank you.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 59, \"text\": \"But dont force yourself.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 60, \"text\": \"You don\'t have to keep a diary just because I bought you one.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 61, \"text\": \"Feel free to write in the diary if you want to, though.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 62, \"text\": \"Well I guess well wrap it up, then.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 63, \"text\": \"Make sure youre not forgetting anything.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 64, \"text\": \"Ill walk out to the corner with you.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(39,71,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"How are you feeling, Lain?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Im doing ok. How about you, Toko-san?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Pretty much as always. I could use a little more time to relax a little, though.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Youre very busy?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Yes Ha, ha. Now our roles are reversed. I feel like you are counseling me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Ha, ha\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Ha, ha. By the way, what did you decide to do about the diary?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I decided to keep a diary.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Wow, thats great! I didnt waste my money right before payday.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Ill pay you for the diary.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Im joking, Im joking.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"But I get paid well anyway.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"For the money I earn, the diary may have been a bit cheap.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"Oh, no.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"This isnt good.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"Im just yacking on about myself.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"But youre funny, Sensei. Youre a lot of fun.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"Ha, ha.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"Well, why dont we begin?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"Lets pick up where we left off last time.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"Have you learned the word ego at school?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 21, \"text\": \"Uh huh. I looked into it. Its about knowing that you are yourself?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 22, \"text\": \"Right.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 23, \"text\": \"People around your age can get unsure about that.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 24, \"text\": \"They ask themselves what kind of person am I? Boys sometimes think that they are heroes and that they will accomplish some superhuman feat someday.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 25, \"text\": \"Girls sometimes imagine that they don\'t belong with their own families.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 26, \"text\": \"They think instead that they are members of a rich elite family, and that a prince on a white steed will come one day to take them away.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 27, \"text\": \"Kids your age sometimes believe these things for real.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 28, \"text\": \"I dont feel that way. I think that Im just me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 29, \"text\": \"But Its hard to tell what you are just by yourself, isnt it?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 30, \"text\": \"When I was younger, I thought that there was a different me, and that somehow I wasn\'t the person I was at the time.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 31, \"text\": \"A different me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 32, \"text\": \"Yes.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 33, \"text\": \"For example, if there was something happening that I didnt like, I wondered why I had to be the one dealing with it.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 34, \"text\": \"I thought there had to be some kind of mistake.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 35, \"text\": \"I thought that someday I would return to the real me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 36, \"text\": \"I also thought things like, if there was a big earthquake, everyone would die, but I would be the only survivor.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 37, \"text\": \"I thought that I was someone special; someone chosen. In another words, I believed in a me that could not be.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 38, \"text\": \"Its funny, isnt it?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 39, \"text\": \"I dont believe that Im anyone chosen. Im ok with being ordinary.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(40,72,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I see.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Thats probably because you are a strong person.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I think I was probably weak and that I was trying to run away because of it.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Do you think Im trying to run away from myself?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I dont think so. But you want to change yourself, dont you?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I just dont want to see any more bad dreams. Thats how I feel.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Could it be that you dont want to be the person who sees the bad dreams?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Maybe you feel that way somewhere deep inside yourself?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Could it be that you are subconsciously trying to construct a me that isnt me?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"What should I do?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Do you think you can accept your dreams?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Accept?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"Right.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"I mean facing the you that you dont want to meet or hear, and then trying to become friends with them.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"I cant.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"I think that all you have to do is listen to the voices.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"See what they are saying and see what they want to do.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"Face them until you understand them and expose them.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"Im scared.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"But youve made it so far.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"Youre still you.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 21, \"text\": \"Youve never had a ghost punch you or had a voice act violently with you, right?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 22, \"text\": \"Maybe these ghosts and voices are trying to be friends with you.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 23, \"text\": \"Ha, ha.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 24, \"text\": \"If you dont see the ghosts again, great.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 25, \"text\": \"But I if you do see them, I think that its important that you have a good attitude and know how to brace yourself.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 26, \"text\": \"If the ghosts show up, just shake it off your shoulders and say, oh, here they are again.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 27, \"text\": \"Im leaving. Im going home.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 28, \"text\": \"Why? Did I say something I shouldnt have?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 29, \"text\": \"I didnt lie to you. I didnt see any ghosts or phantoms. Youre a big jerk!\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 30, \"text\": \"Lain!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(41,73,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Im sorry maam.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I can handle it from here.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"(pause) Lain, Im sorry.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I thought that if I didnt come here personally, you would never see me again.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I came to apologize.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I think I was arrogant about my assumptions about you.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Still, I wanted you to understand and to be comfortable.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I just thought that if you could face your dreams and understand where they were coming from, that they would stop.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Im sorry, Toko-san.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Why?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I lied to you I didnt keep the diary.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Thats ok. I told you that it was all up to you.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"You were trying to be helpful to me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"Thank you. Im grateful that you feel that way. Can you forgive me, Lain?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"Yes.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"Im so glad.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"I was so sad when you walked away from our session.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"I cried.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"I felt so bad.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"I though you didnt like me anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"Toko-san, dont cry.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 21, \"text\": \"Oh.. Its so silly of me to cry over this. Im sorry, Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 22, \"text\": \"Dont cry.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 23, \"text\": \"These are tears of joy, Lain. Im so glad.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 24, \"text\": \"Joy?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 25, \"text\": \"Yes. Tears of joy.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 26, \"text\": \"Im really happy, too. I feel so close to you.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(42,74,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Lets skip counseling today and just relax instead.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"You came all the way out here.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Do you want something to drink?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I cried so much that Im thirsty.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Toko-san, Ill start keeping my diary. Honestly, this time.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Dont force yourself. Youre a kind girl.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Im not forcing myself.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"The diary is for me, after all.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"And the next time I hear the voices, Ill listen to see what they are saying.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Then, Ill tell you what they said, Toko-san.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Thank you, Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Happy birthday, by the way, Toko-san.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"Huh! My birthday?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"I made this for you with my mom.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"Really? Im so happy! Can I open it?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"Sure.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"Cookies! Wow. Theres some tea ready right now. Why dont we have the cookies with some tea?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"Is it good?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"Mmm. It tastes like tea.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"You said that you like tea, so we made the cookies that way.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"Thank you. But then we better have a different kind of tea.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 21, \"text\": \"It wont go with your tea?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 22, \"text\": \"No, not that it wouldnt go with it, but it would be too bad if would couldnt enjoy the tea and cookies as much as possible.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 23, \"text\": \"Should I have made cookies with a different flavor?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 24, \"text\": \"Oh, no, no.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 25, \"text\": \"Not at all!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 26, \"text\": \"But you took all the trouble to make such nice cookies, and I want to enjoy them as much as possible.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 27, \"text\": \"Thats all.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 28, \"text\": \"Really?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 29, \"text\": \"Really. Thanks so much, Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 30, \"text\": \"Sensei, it hurts.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(43,75,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Hello, Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I write in my diary everyday. Sometimes I dont have much to write, though.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Dont worry about it.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"If you force yourself youll just want to give up.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I dont know how many diaries Ive had where I missed entries.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Have you seen any of them since then?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Ive been ok.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Really? Thats good. Theres something I want to confirm with you today.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"What?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"You have really good eyesight, dont you, Lain?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Really good?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Youve had eye exams at school, havent you? Whats your score?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"One-point-five.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"Your eyesight is really even better than that, isnt it?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"But I wanted to have the same score as all the other kids.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"Well theres no point to having the examination then.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"At the last hospital where we used to meet, they examined your eyes, too.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"But they did it differently than at your school.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"They had a machine that measures eyesight automatically.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"The machine only measures as far as three-point-zero, and your score was three-point-zero.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"There are some kids with extremely good eyesight.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 21, \"text\": \"The doctor in charge of your eye-exam spoke with a cancer specialist, who said he saw no problems.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 22, \"text\": \"Oh.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 23, \"text\": \"Lain, what can you see outside the window?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 24, \"text\": \"Trees and a gateway to a shrine in the distance.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 25, \"text\": \"And beyond that?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 26, \"text\": \"Buildings.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 27, \"text\": \"And beyond that?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 28, \"text\": \"Mountains.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 29, \"text\": \"And beyond that?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 30, \"text\": \"I cant see anything further.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 31, \"text\": \"Nothing at all?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 32, \"text\": \"A purplish color that looks like a curtain.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 33, \"text\": \"Thank you.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 34, \"text\": \"Im sorry to pepper you with all these questions.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 35, \"text\": \"I think that you probably see the world in a different way than I do.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 36, \"text\": \"Lain, dont look so glum.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 37, \"text\": \"Its nothing to worry about.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 38, \"text\": \"Its not such a bad thing Im sorry for saying that.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 39, \"text\": \"I guess it is bad thing for you.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 40, \"text\": \"To see things so differently.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 41, \"text\": \"I dont know.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 42, \"text\": \"But I think that Im probably different from everybody else.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 43, \"text\": \"I feel like Im the only person who can hear and see some things.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 44, \"text\": \"It makes me very uncomfortable.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 45, \"text\": \"I think that I will be disliked.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 46, \"text\": \"Is that the reason?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 47, \"text\": \"It might be. I think that youd have to be seen by a specialist.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 48, \"text\": \"No. I want to see you. I dont want to see any of the other doctors here. They all scare me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 49, \"text\": \"Why dont we just keep this as a secret?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 50, \"text\": \"A secret?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 51, \"text\": \"Um hm. It will be our secret until you arent worried about it anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 52, \"text\": \"Is that ok?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 53, \"text\": \"Im your big sister, remember? Im not going to take you anywhere that you will be scared.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 54, \"text\": \"Toko-san.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(44,76,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Good morning, Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Good morning, Toko-san.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Have you seen anything since then?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"No, I havent. Honestly.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Have you heard anything?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Sometimes I hear something very confused.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Very confused? One person? More than one?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"More than one. Men and women.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Are they people you know?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Probably not.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"You said that you heard things from the sky. What do you think is in the sky?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Theres air.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"Uh, huh. And aside from that?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"Clouds. The sun. The stars.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"Do you know about the transmission of radio wavelengths for TV and cell phones?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"Yes. The information travels wirelessly?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"Right. The information flies through the sky.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"Am I hearing that information?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"Hmm. It might be that you imagine you are hearing that information.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"Theres a sickness like that?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"There is.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 21, \"text\": \"Its called delusion.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 22, \"text\": \"Its a symptom of schizophrenia and neurosis.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 23, \"text\": \"Sometimes, if you are focusing much too much on something or are getting very stressed, it can bring out those kind of symptoms.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 24, \"text\": \"But\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 25, \"text\": \"But?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 26, \"text\": \"Usually, when people say they hear things, what they hear is more closely associated with themselves.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 27, \"text\": \"For instance, they hear voices that bad-mouth them.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 28, \"text\": \"Delusion of persecution?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 29, \"text\": \"Right.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 30, \"text\": \"Youve been studying up on this stuff.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 31, \"text\": \"Ok. Ill fill you in a little more on this.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 32, \"text\": \"The definition of delusion is taking a mistaken idea and believing in your own mind that it is correct.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 33, \"text\": \"But for you, Lain, you say that you might have felt or sensed something.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 34, \"text\": \"A person who is really delusional tends to have conviction that his delusions are real.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 35, \"text\": \"But you dont have that.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 36, \"text\": \"You have thoughts, considerations.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 37, \"text\": \"Considerations?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 38, \"text\": \"You can forget that word if youd like.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 39, \"text\": \"As I mentioned before, a delusion is generally something intertwined with ones self.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 40, \"text\": \"There really arent any delusions that have nothing to do with someone personally.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 41, \"text\": \"Im not delusional?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 42, \"text\": \"Fundamentally, no.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 43, \"text\": \"Still, there are all sorts of delusions, and if you try to pin one of them onto someone, you may start pinning other ones on that person, too.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(45,77,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"What could happen?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Hmm.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"There is a delusion some people have that they are being influenced by something.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"The delusion that the radio or TV or cell phones are trying to influence them somehow.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"The delusion that TV and cell phones have the power to touch them physically.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"You said that you thought you were being touched by something, didnt you, Lain?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Uh, huh.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"It might not even be a delusion.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"There is an actual medical condition that makes people very sensitive physically.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"But you said that you dont feel like you are yourself, didnt you, Lain?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"That makes me think that you have the delusion that nothing exists.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"That you think you arent real and that existence isnt real.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"This can come as the result of poor self-esteem.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"Poor self-esteem?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"Its the feeling that one is worthless.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"Its similar to the delusion of persecution we were talking about.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"Im really sick.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"There are other kinds of delusions.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"I dont want to listen anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"Some people have the delusion that they have a special, unique sickness.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"Its the sickness of thinking they have a sickness, when they really arent sick.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 21, \"text\": \"I think that what you have, Lain, is mostly to do with this kind of delusion.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 22, \"text\": \"The sickness of thinking that I am sick when Im not sick?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 23, \"text\": \"Yes.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 24, \"text\": \"I think that you have poor self-esteem, and that a small insecurity manifests itself in nightmares, and makes you think that you are sick.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 25, \"text\": \"Can I be cured?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 26, \"text\": \"Sure!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 27, \"text\": \"After all, youre not sick in the first place.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 28, \"text\": \"Im sorry to have alarmed you.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 29, \"text\": \"Still, if you dont understand psychiatry well, you can use it to make all sorts of misguided conclusions.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 30, \"text\": \"You can diagnose yourself as being sick.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 31, \"text\": \"Most people go to the doctor when they or someone they know cant carry on their day-to-day activities.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 32, \"text\": \"They come in to see a doctor and they are diagnosed or treated, and they are diagnosed sometimes as sick.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 33, \"text\": \"So for someone like you, who can continue her own day-to-day activities without a problem, we cant really say that you are sick unless somethings bad enough that you to need hospitalization.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(46,78,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Am I sick because I came to the hospital?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Well, you can carry on with your life, but youre troubled, arent you Lain?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Its the job of a counselor to help with that.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Are you a counselor, Toko-san? You said before that youre a doctor.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Im a counselor and a doctor.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"How are the two different?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Well, both jobs have to do with helping people with psychological problems.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Theyre similar in the sense that they have the same goals.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"But the difference is that as a counselor I care for patients differently than I do as a doctor, and that each job has different qualifications.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Each job has its strengths and weaknesses, and I think its best when I can make their strengths compliment each other.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Thats why Im a doctor and a counselor.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Are you a doctor or a counselor when you see me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"Im a counselor. I think its better for me to be a counselor when I see you.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"Im not mentally ill? You said that the things I see are hallucinations.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"Its true that hallucinations and delusions are symptoms of mental illness, and this is just my hunch, but you dont seem to be mentally ill to me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"Do I pay too much attention to things?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"Yes, I think thats probably right.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"I think your tendency to observe things and listen to thing very carefully might be stressing you out.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"What can I do about it, Toko-san?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"Well even if I told you not to mind things too much, youre going to mind things.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"I don\'t mind anymore. Im getting used to this. Still, I can\'t get used to that.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 21, \"text\": \"That?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 22, \"text\": \"Im not the me that I am right now.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 23, \"text\": \"What kind of Lain are you?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 24, \"text\": \"Im me. That person is, too.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 25, \"text\": \"Why do you feel that way?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 26, \"text\": \"I dont know. Have you ever thought that you arent you, Toko-san?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 27, \"text\": \"Looking back on myself in the past, Ive wondered what I was doing sometimes.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 28, \"text\": \"But Ive never thought at the time that I wasnt me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 29, \"text\": \"Do you feel that there are two of you, Lain?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 30, \"text\": \"No. Im me and Im not me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 31, \"text\": \"Thats mysterious.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 32, \"text\": \"But if you feel that way, that must be true for you.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 33, \"text\": \"You dont have to feel that youre mistaken.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 34, \"text\": \"But it isnt usual.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(47,79,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Youre really yearning all the time, arent you, Lain?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Probably\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Im envious.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Human perception is a wild thing.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"If you start feeling something, you start believing it.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I don\'t know how to explain to anyone that I am really me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"But being able to question that sense of self is a special talent.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I dont want a talent like that.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Yeah.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Im sure you feel really strongly that way right now.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"But I feel that it can be a good thing for you too.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"I don\'t understand it well right now, but I think that if you can include and accept that as part of yourself, it would help you in the long run.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"I wont change?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"I dont know.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"You might change naturally and stop having nightmares.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"If that happens, youd be like most other kids.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"But I wont know if Ive gotten better. I might have nightmares again.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"Yeah. But things will change from now on.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"What do you mean?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"I mean that youre not alone. Im here and you can talk to me about things.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"Thats true, Toko-san.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(48,80,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Good morning, Toko-san.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Good morning. How are you? Have you been feeling healthy?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Uh huh. I thought about the things you talked about last month and Ive somehow been feeling better.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Oh, thats great.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Actually, though, its against the rules to talk about the things we talked about last month.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"In some people it can trigger something irreversible.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Irreversible?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Their sickness could worsen, and sometimes, patients can hurt themselves physically.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Suicide?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Well, that would be the worst-case scenario.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I dont want to die.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Of course not!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"Far from it.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"But when people become troubled emotionally, they start to see things and act differently than you or I would.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"See things differently?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"They can lose their fear of dying or hurting themselves.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"In fact they start to feel that dying or getting hurt are very good things.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"You cant understand that, can you?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"I am afraid of those things.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"Sure! Me too. Were the same way. Thats normal.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"Ok.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(49,81,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Have you seen or heard anything since then?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"No.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"See!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"It was a state of mind, Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I think that you probably wont see them again, but if you do, dont get discouraged.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Youll get over it gradually.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I wont get better right away?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Hmm. I dont know. How old were you when you started having problems with them?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I was eleven.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"So its been over a year now. During that time, how often did it happen?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I dont remember once.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Sometimes, even if there doesn\'t seem to be an explanation for it immediately, these things may go away.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"But if you decide that theyve gone away completely and become complacent, theres a chance that they may come back.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"I cant say for certain that that will happen with you, but even if you dont see them for a while, Id like you to continue what youve been doing up till now.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"Do you want to stop coming here, Lain?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"No. I like seeing you.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"Thank you.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"I guess that theres no problem, then.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"Youre doing well, but youll promise me that you will keep coming here?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"Yes. In exchange, I want you to teach me some things.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"Why?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 21, \"text\": \"For homework?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 22, \"text\": \"Sure.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 23, \"text\": \"You wont believe it, but I was pretty sharp in junior high school.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 24, \"text\": \"Ha, ha.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 25, \"text\": \"Learning to read and write was tough, though.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 26, \"text\": \"I dont mean that. I want to know more about your work. Is that ok?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 27, \"text\": \"Hmm.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 28, \"text\": \"I don\'t think its a very good idea, but if youre really curious, ok. Learning about things that make you curious is a great way to study.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 29, \"text\": \"But you have to make time for your schoolwork, too.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 30, \"text\": \"Ill promise to teach you about my work if you promise to do your schoolwork.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 31, \"text\": \"Can you promise me that?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 32, \"text\": \"Yes, I promise.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 33, \"text\": \"And if you break your promise\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 34, \"text\": \"Ill whack you with a blowfish!\", \"actor\": \"Lain and Toko together\"}]'),(50,82,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"You are a counselor and a psychiatrist, Toko-san?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"And a psychiatrist is someone who heals mental illnesses?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Uh huh. Put simply, Im a doctor of the mind. As I mentioned before, mental illness is very complex.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"What is mental illness?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Basically, a persons mind becomes disturbed for some reason, and the person is unable to continue functioning.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"What sort of reason, for instance?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"There can be many reasons.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Problems with a living environment or work environment can be reasons.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Sudden, psychological shock can also be a reason.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"The sudden death of a well-loved pet can trigger mental illness.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Sometimes people become mentally ill because of something that happens to them physically.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"A car accident or some other kind of physical trauma can be a cause.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"Also, people who drink too much can damage the function of their brains.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"Alcoholism?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"Exactly.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"Youve been studying!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"If you drink too much the alcohol content in your blood will rise.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"Youve seen drunk people wobble around without balance, havent you?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"Theyre in an alcoholic stupor.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"But normal people arent that way, are they?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"No, they can be.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 21, \"text\": \"It takes about 24 hours for alcohol to leave the human body.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 22, \"text\": \"If you drink a lot everyday for a year or soif you stay drunk long enoughyoull your perception will start to change.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 23, \"text\": \"Your brain will start to deteriorate.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 24, \"text\": \"Thats scary.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 25, \"text\": \"It is scary. I still have some sake now and then, though.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 26, \"text\": \"Isnt that dangerous?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 27, \"text\": \"Ha, ha.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 28, \"text\": \"Oh, a little bit.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 29, \"text\": \"And smoking is bad too.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 30, \"text\": \"But having a drink with friends every now and then can help relieve stress.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 31, \"text\": \"Relieving stress is very important for the bodys health.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 32, \"text\": \"I dont understand what stress is.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 33, \"text\": \"Remember when you didnt like coming here at first?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 34, \"text\": \"Yes.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 35, \"text\": \"Stress is what we call the cause of that discomfort.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 36, \"text\": \"Youre glad that the discomfort is gone, arent you?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 37, \"text\": \"Yes. What other kinds of mental illness are there?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 38, \"text\": \"Could you excuse me? Ive been talking so much and Im a little thirsty.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(51,83,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I wanted to ask last time, but why do have that kind of hairstyle?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Its weird?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"No, its great! You really look good that way. Is it a popular look at your school?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"No. Its just my own style.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"You mentioned that you want to be like other kids. Why do you have a unique look?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"It comes from the right, and probably, thats why it goes out of the left. Thats why...\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"It works a little bit like a magic charm, then. I used have a magic charm, too.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"You did, Toko-san?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Sure.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"It didnt have to do with hairstyle, but I used to have a lucky rabbits foot.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I used to believe that it would keep me safe and happy, and I tied it to my backpack.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Looking back, it seems so ghastly.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"To tie a little bunnys foot to my backpack.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"But then again, believing in the rabbits foot really made me feel safer.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"A magic charm?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"Yeah.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"Your hair looks really good, though, Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"If you had a hairstyle like everyone elses, it wouldnt be like you.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"I think you look great the way you are.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(52,84,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"You know about neurosis? Wow, Lain. Youre going to have to start counseling me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I know the word, not its meaning.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"What kind of image?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"The mind changes and becomes distorted?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Yes. Youve got the general idea.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Thats awful. You wont teach me anymore?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"No.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Im really telling you that you got the general idea.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Neurosis is a state in which there is nothing wrong with a person physically, yet the person has irrational fears and perceives threats.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"This places a lot of stress on the person and makes her feel sick.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Its only inside of their heads?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"We used to think so.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"But after a lot of research, we think that an imbalance of the autonomic nerves in the brain is related to it.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"What I mean is, something is wrong in the body, too.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"We used to categorize physical symptoms as psychosomatic.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"But weve been finding more and more that conditions we thought were only of the mind involve the body itself.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"Psychosomatic?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"Oh, Lain, if ask so many questions, your head is going to explode!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"Youve heard about people who lose a lot of weight because of stress, or go bald?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"Thats psychosomatic.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"Lain, you dont, by any chance\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 21, \"text\": \"No, I dont have that kind of problem.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 22, \"text\": \"Oh, Im relieved. That was hasty of me!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(53,85,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Who decides the names of diseases?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Various doctors.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"But we have general criterions.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"We have the ICD and the DSM, which are international standards for the definition of mental diseases.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"We know that if a person has a certain set of symptoms, we can consult these standards and find the exact name of the disease the person is suffering from.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"As you know, the mind can be a difficult thing to understand.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"For that reason, psychiatrists have publications, and we communicate all the time, sharing our data and our understanding of mental illness.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"We accumulate data and categorize it so that we can diagnose patients as correctly as possible.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Theres mental illness you don\'t understand? Not even you?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"To tell you the truth, we dont understand much of this at all.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"If there has been a successful treatment method for a patient with a certain disease in the past, we can apply that treatment method toward a patient suffering from the same disease in the present.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Much of this has to do with experience.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"You do this even if you dont know if a person can be cured?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"Right.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"You cant tell if a person will be cured.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"We can only try our best to heal and help with our experience from the past.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"Thats usually the case.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"But from the point of view of the patient, knowing if one will become better is very important.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"In fact, the understanding of the mechanisms behind getting better is an area of study of its own.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"I see. It would be so much better if we could understand everything.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(54,86,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Do you have many memories from your childhood?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Memories? Do you mean records?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Well, memories and records arent exactly the same.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Don\'t think about it too much.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"If youve traveled somewhere during summer vacation\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I havent traveled anywhere during summer vacation.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Im sorry.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"In my youth, both of my parents worked, so I didnt get to travel very much.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I didnt like it when I went back to school after vacation and other kids would ask me where I went or what I did during the summer.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Whats the difference between a memory and a record?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"From a medical standpoint, a record is something documented that lists exactly what happened, when and where.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"A memory is more subjective.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"Its what you remember personally.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"Its something in your mind that you can access from time to time.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"But Lain, doesnt all this stuff bore you?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"No. How does a memory enter the brain?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"How? Thats a pretty complicated subject. Are you sure you want to get into it?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(55,87,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"There are different kinds of memories.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"First of all, theres ones memory of oneself.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"You know what self- understanding is?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"You know that you are a girl named Lain with a certain face and height and weight?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Thats all recorded at a molecular level.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Aside from the brain, there are places throughout the body that carry residues of things that have happened.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"You know that if you get cut, you bleed, but if you wait a while, it gets scab and heals?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"That has to do with information stored in cells going to work.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Take a look at athletes and people who have gone through intense physical training.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"They seem to do things effortlessly.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Thats because their bodies have their own recollection or memory.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"If you generate a recording, you have a memory?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"You might be able to say that sometimes, but not always.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"Humans are haphazard and unpredictable, arent they?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"I dont remember everything that happened to me as a kid precisely.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"I have happy memories of times I spent with my family, but my family might not have happy memories of those times at all.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"I may have had misperceptions in the moment, or I may have remembered things incorrectly and by mistake.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"But we all walk around with memories, thinking that what we remember is what actually happened.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"Suppose you meet an old friend that you havent seen in a long time.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"Dont you remember the things you used to do with that person right away?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"Your memory has a way of linking things together.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 21, \"text\": \"If you cant link things together, youre sick?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 22, \"text\": \"Well, there is something called memory impediment.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 23, \"text\": \"People who have this cant remember things that happened only moments ago.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 24, \"text\": \"They have no idea of how things in the past took place.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 25, \"text\": \"They dont know what happened and in what order.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 26, \"text\": \"Since they dont want anyone to know that they dont remember things, they often make up stories about the past to fool people.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 27, \"text\": \"Humans are complex.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 28, \"text\": \"We do all sorts of things.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 29, \"text\": \"Youve seen senile old people on TV shows, havent you?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 30, \"text\": \"As humans, there are some things we cant do anything about.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 31, \"text\": \"Things we cant do anything about?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 32, \"text\": \"Im not saying that youre sick, Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 33, \"text\": \"There are things we cant do anything about, arent there?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 34, \"text\": \"We cant flap our arms and fly, can we?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 35, \"text\": \"There are memories in the body and the brain?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 36, \"text\": \"There are still many things we dont understand.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 37, \"text\": \"The human brain is made up of many different things.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 38, \"text\": \"When something is recorded there, there is a change that takes place that becomes the foundation for memories.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 39, \"text\": \"I dont understand.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 40, \"text\": \"Yeah.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 41, \"text\": \"When you go to high school and college, you can study up on all this stuff.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 42, \"text\": \"But its good that you have a healthy curiosity.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 43, \"text\": \"I dont think youre sick, Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 44, \"text\": \"I feel that my memories arent my memories.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 45, \"text\": \"Sure! I feel that way sometimes, too.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 46, \"text\": \"Even when its me. But I dont remember anything else.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 47, \"text\": \"Youve just forgotten something, thats all.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 48, \"text\": \"Didnt I say that human beings are haphazard and unpredictable?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 49, \"text\": \"We remember things the way we want to remember them and often forget what we want to.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 50, \"text\": \"Thats being human.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 51, \"text\": \"Thats normal.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 52, \"text\": \"Normal?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 53, \"text\": \"Yes. You dwell on things too much, Lain. All those things are normal.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(56,88,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I wondered if your name has anything to do with R. D. Laing. Oh, it couldnt, could it?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"R.D. Laing?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Its a persons name.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"An English psychiatrist.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"He was an unusual person.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"The titles of some of his books are very interesting.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"One of them is: I Love, Love, Really Love.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I Love, Love, Really Love?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I read it when I was in college and I dont remember much of it, but its about two loversa man and a womanand the woman asks the man if he loves her.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"And?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Well of course, the man replies that he loves her.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"But the woman isn\'t satisfied, and asks more and more questions.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"I dont understand.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"OK. Lets see. Do you like me, Lain?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"Yes, I do.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"More than your dad? More than your mom?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"Yes.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"That makes me happy. Do you mean it?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"Yes I do.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"Are you happy when youre here?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"I dont really understand, but I probably am.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 21, \"text\": \"Do you like talking to me?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 22, \"text\": \"Yes.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 23, \"text\": \"What do you like about me?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 24, \"text\": \"Youre kind and you listen to me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 25, \"text\": \"Which do you like more? That Im kind, or that I listen?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 26, \"text\": \"Which?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 27, \"text\": \"Yes, which?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 28, \"text\": \"I like you because youre kind.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 29, \"text\": \"How am I kind to you?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 30, \"text\": \"You dont get angry and youre polite.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 31, \"text\": \"But there are lots of people besides me who dont get angry at you.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 32, \"text\": \"There are lots of people who are polite to you.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 33, \"text\": \"Arent there?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 34, \"text\": \"Do you really like me?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 35, \"text\": \"I dont really know.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 36, \"text\": \"Do I have to think about all this stuff?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 37, \"text\": \"Lets stop this.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 38, \"text\": \"I feel like I might start to not like you.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(57,89,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Im sorry. I just was trying to explain this issue to you.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I like you too Lain, though Im not sure why.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I suppose I just enjoy talking to you. Thats it.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Its probably just because I like my job!\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I just thought it had to do with you, but I guess not.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"It is enough for me to be able to understand my feelings.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I can never read your mind, so I can never know that you like me as much as I like you.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Sounds lonely\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Im sorry, but you know, this is one of the ways for me to know that.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Im so happy with you saying that you like me.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Are you happy with me saying I like you?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Yes, indeed.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"Yes, that is enough. Lain, I like you.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"But still, as you can never comprehend all of me, it is impossible for me to know everything about you.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"If we could know everything about each other, I could be you and vice versa.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"I mean you do not have to be Lain unless we are different people.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"I really like Lain even though Lain is hard to understand sometimes.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"You like the mysterious Lain?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"Well, I like Lain who I dont know very well. Of course, that is not all I like.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"I want to know everything about you!!\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"So do I! But its impossible.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 21, \"text\": \"Impossible?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 22, \"text\": \"Yes. That is because even I dont know who I am!\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 23, \"text\": \"Well, I dont know how to explain this to you. Lain is Lain and I am me.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 24, \"text\": \"Actually it might be still impossible even if we became the same person.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 25, \"text\": \"The same person?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 26, \"text\": \"Yes, Lain and I are exactly the same!\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 27, \"text\": \"We see the same things, have the same ideas and take same actions.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 28, \"text\": \"Everything.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 29, \"text\": \"Even our looks are the same!\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 30, \"text\": \"In this situation, there is only an identity that you KEEP, isn\'t there?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 31, \"text\": \"Yet even if such an identification is gone.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 32, \"text\": \"If you thought Here is Lain, then I cannot exist there.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 33, \"text\": \"The same thing can happen to you!\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 34, \"text\": \"That is why its impossible to understand each other at the same time.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 35, \"text\": \"But what if you would answer every question I ask.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 36, \"text\": \"Still, it would be impossible?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 37, \"text\": \"Right, but they are not all possible questions, are they?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 38, \"text\": \"I need time to answer those questions and those answers could be changed eventually, such as I used to think one thing, but now I have changed my mind  something like that.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 39, \"text\": \"It\'s impossible after all, isnt it?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 40, \"text\": \"Yes, I wish I could go inside your mind and answer everything you want to know\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}]'),(58,90,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Are you happy at your school?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Yes, I am!\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"What makes you so happy!\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"You know, playing and talking with my best friend.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Thats good! It is a good thing to like school, isnt it?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Were you happy?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Not really, because I didnt have many friends there.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"You feel sad without friends at school.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Yeah Im sorry\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"About what?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"That story reminds you of a bad memory.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Well, it certainly wasnt good memory, but thats OK.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"I actually feel sorry for my past, but my current job makes me think that was a good experience for me.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"Good experience?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"Yes.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"For example, such an experience is sometimes so useful to analyze the psychology of those who doesnt want to go to school.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"It sounds difficult.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"Im sorry, Im talking about myself now! Whenever I talk about my job, I tend to get lost in it.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"I guess I would make a better patient.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"Ok, lets change the subject. Well, what is your best friend like?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"She is really cheerful and nice to me. Im really happy around her.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 21, \"text\": \"What\'s her name?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 22, \"text\": \"Misato.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 23, \"text\": \"OK Misato. What do you usually do together?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 24, \"text\": \"We read books together at her place and I listen to her playing violin sometimes.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 25, \"text\": \"Wow, she can play the violin.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 26, \"text\": \"Awesome!\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 27, \"text\": \"She must be a good friend.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 28, \"text\": \"Why dont you come over with her next time?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 29, \"text\": \"But she is so shy.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 30, \"text\": \"So shy?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 31, \"text\": \"Maybe Ill ask her anyway. Im guessing she wouldnt want to.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 32, \"text\": \"Well, I wish she could.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}]'),(59,91,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Touko-san, deja vu isnt an illness, is it?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"No.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"You may also feel its the first time youve seen a scene which youve seen before.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Both situations have nothing to do with a disease.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Even normal people sometimes have an experience of deja vu.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"What a relief! I feel better now.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Do you feel anything else when you experience deja vu?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Time is strange for some reason. I cant figure out if time is fast or slow.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Do you feel its real or kind of ordinary?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Well, it could be or could not be I dont know maybe not\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Is it nebular? Or you just cant comprehend\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"I just feel something is different.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"Even though I recognize that I am playing in my house, I feel like it isnt my house.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"And even though I dont know where it is, when I play at a park that Ive never seen, for me it seems like the place I usually use.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"Strange Do you feel comfortable or uneasy when you are there?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"I dont know, but Lain was laughing when it happened.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"Not yourself but Lain?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"I cant explain very well but it was Lain\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"Where were you at that time?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"Lets see I dont know, because I was just watching her\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"I mean, where from did you observe her?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 21, \"text\": \"Like, were you standing on the ground, or you could you see her from the sky?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 22, \"text\": \"Well I dont know It was like I saw myself on the TV I guess\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 23, \"text\": \"Lain, are you all right? You dont have to bring it back by force. Im sorry.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 24, \"text\": \"I feel compelled to ask questions. OK, thats all for today!\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 25, \"text\": \"How do you express it in technical jargon?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 26, \"text\": \"No, lets stop for now.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 27, \"text\": \"I really want to know about myself!\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 28, \"text\": \"OK, so this is the last lesson.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 29, \"text\": \"In technical jargon, we call it alienation of perception. It means that you experience something as if somebody else experienced it.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 30, \"text\": \"Its an illness, isnt it?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 31, \"text\": \"There is one called depersonalization which is that you cannot feel yourself, but you couldnt have it.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 32, \"text\": \"So stop worrying about it.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 33, \"text\": \"You cant prove that I dont.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 34, \"text\": \"Yes, but it doesnt worry you. So I can say that youre not sick.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 35, \"text\": \"Well, I shouldnt have said that; it just makes you worried.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 36, \"text\": \"I guess I made a mistake\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 37, \"text\": \"No, you didnt.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 38, \"text\": \"You didnt make any mistakes because I insisted that you should answer my question.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 39, \"text\": \"Still, I want to study a lot in order to be like you, Touko-san.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 40, \"text\": \"Lain\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}]'),(60,92,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"The ego is your sense of who you are, isnt it?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Yes, but more technically phrased, the ego is a part of the mind you use to experience as yourself and to recognize yourself.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Do you get it?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Not at all.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Ok, so you have an idea that you are Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"In such the structural element, the EGO is right there.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Linguistically, myself describes all of you, right?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Ego is, however, one of the parts of your mind you use to recognize that all of experiences I have had were mine.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Saying its just to realize that you are yourself is somewhat better to understand?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"I can get the last part, but it is still beyond my understanding.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I like your honesty.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"So the girl, Lain, has various emotions, such as kindness, loneliness and things like that.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"Now the EGO is what is left when you dont feel any emotions.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"I guess I understand a little\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"For example, the Lain who woke up this morning and what Lain is now here are the same, right?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"Right.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"What Lain will be tomorrow should be the same as those.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"I guess so.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"I mean if your ego works properly, you can recognize that you exist continuously and confirm that that existence is myself. If your ego doesnt work properly\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"If it doesnt?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"We call such a situation identity disorder in the medical field.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 21, \"text\": \"On the other hand, there is also an isolation disorder which means you think that you are not yourself.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 22, \"text\": \"He, he, they sound like bad diseases, dont they?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 23, \"text\": \"Yet anyone your age usually doesnt complete his or her ego until later.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 24, \"text\": \"You just can gradually recognize yourself with age.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 25, \"text\": \"So is it wrong to think that I understand myself at my age?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 26, \"text\": \"It just happens to be that such things happen all the time.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}]'),(61,93,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"If I became sick, what would you do for it?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"If you were sick?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I mean if\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Well, since you are still young, I wouldnt use any medical treatment for such minor symptoms the way one uses medicine to cure disease.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Why wouldnt you use them?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Lain, you already have the power to recover your health from disease.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"If you depend on using those medicines, however, your body becomes weaker.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Usually children shouldnt take medicine too much anyway.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"So what are you going to do?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Lets see I will use psychotherapy to help you, like talking with you as we do now.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Just talking?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Hmm, its difficult to explain it. For example, we have a program to recover people from alcoholism.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"In this program, they discuss and present what make them drink so much and listen to each others stories.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"We call it group therapy. I dont like it though.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"Why you dont like it?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"I think people who regain their health from those group therapies would make the same mistakes later.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"They think that they can recover themselves from alcoholism simply by group conversation, but when they are alone, they will start drinking again.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"Ive seen this happen a lot.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"So what would you do?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"I try to talk one-on-one as I do with you, Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"And?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 21, \"text\": \"And then, I suggest those patients to think about themselves.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 22, \"text\": \"I have nothing particular to support them but I try to analyze what they think on neutral ground.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 23, \"text\": \"This helps them to recognize what is wrong with themselves, and then they try to recover their own health.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 24, \"text\": \"We call it non-supportive psychotherapy.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 25, \"text\": \"If they start recognizing there is a problem, it means they are already fine.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 26, \"text\": \"Is that enough to recover them from diseases? Sound simple!\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 27, \"text\": \"Right, it sounds so simple.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 28, \"text\": \"In fact, however, those things are more complicated and difficult to do than you think.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 29, \"text\": \"Difficult?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 30, \"text\": \"(yawn) Im sorry. I need more sleep.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 31, \"text\": \"You must be tired. Should you take a break?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 32, \"text\": \"(yawn)\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}]'),(62,94,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"When you get sick in the head, your head is really sick?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"The brain isnt the only part of the body involved in mental illness, but it is very important.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"We know that many types of disease occur because of trauma to the brain.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"When the brain is injured, something is broken?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"The human brain is very complex, and there are many things we dont understand about it.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"We know that some parts of the brain seem to have a certain function.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"We know a little about where and when things take place in the brain.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Memories are stored in the hippocampus.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Yes.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"There is the frontal lobe and the occipital lobe, and there are many other parts of the brain that have different functions.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Many chemical processes take place in the brain.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"When they do, a lot of information is exchanged.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"Thats how the brain gets sick?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"Sometimes the brain does get sick that way.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"If there is an abnormal change in the brains chemical process, or if the parts of the brain responsible for processing information are physically damaged and not working properly, there could be disease.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"We call this kind of disease organic psychosis.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"Is this hard to understand?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"I understand. People have their brainwaves tested and have CAT scans to check for it.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"Are they teaching you that at school already? Did you teach yourself?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"I checked it out on the Web. I had a test done before, and I was curious.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"Lain, if youre doing all this research, you dont have to see me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 21, \"text\": \"No, its not like that. I learn a lot from you. It isnt like the things I learn from books.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 22, \"text\": \"Im sorry, Lain. Im not feeling very well.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 23, \"text\": \"Is there brain research at this research center?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 24, \"text\": \"Yes.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 25, \"text\": \"What kind of research?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 26, \"text\": \"Im not a specialist and I dont work in that area, so I cant say anything specifically.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 27, \"text\": \"But its on the Web. All sorts of research takes place.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 28, \"text\": \"Lain, can I ask you a favor? Im not feeling very well. Can we end for today?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 29, \"text\": \"Im sorry, Toko-san.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(63,95,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"What kind of research do you do?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Research? I never mentioned that\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": 