und.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"But you said that I could talk. I want to know about you.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"How is finding out about me going to help you? Do you just want to irritate me?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"You really didnt like my questions?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"No, I didnt!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 21, \"text\": \"I want you to leave things alone.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 22, \"text\": \"I dont want you trying to get inside my head.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 23, \"text\": \"Thats what I think.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 24, \"text\": \"Arent you sad to be alone?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 25, \"text\": \"Im not alone!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 26, \"text\": \"I am not you!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 27, \"text\": \"You are Lain, arent you?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 28, \"text\": \"Youre the proper, reserved, sad girl without much self-confidence, arent you?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 29, \"text\": \"No, thats not me. I think my personality is much different from that.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 30, \"text\": \"Then who are you?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 31, \"text\": \"Im Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(72,104,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I felt really good today.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Thats really great, Toko-san.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Im starting to feel worse, though. I cant tell whats bothering me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Is it something vague? Something about feeling dormant?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"When youre feeling happy, dont you sometimes feel worried about when it might come to an end?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Is that a symptom of an intermittent flow of thought?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I cant imagine myself being happy.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"You can imagine yourself being unhappy?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I suppose. But I cant get rid of the worry.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Is there something I can do?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"What would I want to seek for from you? Why me from you?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Are you too proud to tell me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"It has nothing to do with pride. Why dont you tell me what you think is going on with me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"Youre just Toko-san. Youre yourself.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"Thats right. I better get to my reports. If you want, you can stay around here, but I have to go.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"Why?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"Because there is something I have to do right now.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"There is something that I can only do now.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"I have to continue my research.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"That makes you happy?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"Yes, it does. My number one goal is to continue doing the research that I enjoy.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 21, \"text\": \"So thats number one?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 22, \"text\": \"No.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 23, \"text\": \"Thats not what I mean.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 24, \"text\": \"Seeing you is very important, too.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 25, \"text\": \"Its very important to me that everything goes well.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 26, \"text\": \"But I have to do things in order.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 27, \"text\": \"Im glad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(73,105,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Are you troubled about anything?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"No, Im not. How about you, Toko-san?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Sometimes. I feel like something bad might happen.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Youre feeling delusional?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Yes, but unlike with you, it isnt a strange delusional problem with perception.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I wonder if thats true.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"But how about the feelings you have about that man?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Arent those feelings delusional?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Who is that man?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"The man youre thinking about right now.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"You can tell what Im thinking.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Wow!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"You have super powers?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"Is that why you poke fun at me sometimes?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"But Im connected to you, Toko-san.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"Connected? In what way?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"It probably wouldnt make sense if I tried to explain it to you.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"Thats called psychosis, Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"Believing yourself to be a unique chosen person or that you are God.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"Thats a serious disease.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"Im sick. How about you?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 21, \"text\": \"Im not sick. Im\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(74,106,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"You dont have much energy.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Im tired.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Are you tired of doing miscellaneous chores?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Is someone having you do waste your time with small tasks?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Yeah. I do feel that way sometimes.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Do you think you have some kind of psychological condition?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Do you think you might have caught something from me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Ha, ha.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Why do you think Im like this? I know and understand the things I am talking about.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Youre ok, Toko-san. Youll be better by tomorrow.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Ill be better?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Youll be in a world where you dont suffer.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"Am I myself when I am by myself or when Im with you?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"Youre always yourself. Even when you doubt my existence.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"I doubt your existence?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"Yes. You dont want to believe that I exist.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"Why would I have a problem like that because I treat you?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"There is information you wouldnt understand now. You arent doing well psychologically.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"Information I wouldnt understand now? But I want to know now.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"Yes. But it would be too difficult for you to understand now.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"Youre thinking about whats best for me, arent you, Lain?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 21, \"text\": \"Of course, I am. I like you.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(75,107,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"A rumor?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Does it bother you?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Someone is spreading rumors about you?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Is that a delusion of persecution?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Some other kind of delusion?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Well, it might just be a lack of self-confidence.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Why do you have so much confidence, even when youre sick, Lain?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Im sick. Whats the name of my disease? Schizophrenia? Manic depression? Something else?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"You arent any of those things.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"You have pathomimesis.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Thats what you call the imitation of disease.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Then Im not really sick?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"You dont exist.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"I just think that youre here.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"Everyone has been tricked.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"Weve all been shown some glimpse of your existence.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"Thats why no one really remembers you.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"Its not like you to be mad. Some of us dont seem to exist, though. Which are you?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"I think that you think Im here.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"Youre a delusion that created a delusion.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"All these things, your constructed diseases and your voices, are delusions.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 21, \"text\": \"How about me? Am I here?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 22, \"text\": \"Thats why I have to heal you!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 23, \"text\": \"Youre so serious. But youre an elite. Youve been chosen.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 24, \"text\": \"Thats right.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 25, \"text\": \"Im trying hard to be here.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 26, \"text\": \"I would rather have been out playing and fooling around, but Ive gone to school and studied and worked hard to get here.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 27, \"text\": \"I feel sorry for you, Toko-san.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(76,108,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Are you ok, Toko-san.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Yes. Im hanging in there. Sometimes I dont feel so good.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"You think too much, Toko-san. You pay too much attention to whats going on around you.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I have things to think about. Work. Romance.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Is a love life necessary?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I think its a very important part of life.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Does a woman need a man?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Not just because shes a woman. If that were true, a man would need a woman.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"It would be obsessive to think that a woman must have a man, Toko-san. You can live on your own.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"But wouldnt that be sad? I cant stand to be sad. How about you? How about you, Lain?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I would get sad, too.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(77,109,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"You dont want to do anything? How about your research?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"No one will want to read my paper anyway.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Whats wrong? Its not like you to play a victim.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Not like me! What am I?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Youre just Toko-san, Toko-san.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Ive been severed from society. Im no longer connected.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Thats not true. Im connected to you. Im connected to society. Thats why youre connected, too.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Somethings wrong with me, isnt there?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"The times when I talk to you and the time I spend with everything else are separate.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"From your point of view, my life must be a contradiction.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"My point of view?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"From your point of view, this world doesnt exist.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"No. Thats not true. Im connected to this world.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"I cant take it anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"I cant even stand this moment.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"Thats not all.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"My memories of tomorrowthe memories Ill have in the future are in disarray.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"Is this a delusion caused by worrying?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"Am I experiencing something I shouldnt be experiencing?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"Thats you, isnt it?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"It is me! Because it is me!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 21, \"text\": \"Wouldnt you be better off if you were just being yourself?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 22, \"text\": \"I cant understand my sense of self from moment to moment!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 23, \"text\": \"The judgment you have exactly at that moment is you, Toko-san. The rest is\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 24, \"text\": \"The rest is\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 25, \"text\": \"Ordinary data.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(78,110,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Concerning diagnosis: The client lives in a nuclear family with her mother and father.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Both parents are middle to upper class and financially well-to-do.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"The parents have a stable relationship.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"They do not seem to have mental health problems.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Concerning family history of illness, according to the parents as well as the database at our center, there was no neurosis, mental illness, suicidality or consanguineous marriage in her family.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(79,111,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"She hasnt had any significant problems from the time of birth.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Even at this point, she doesnt have any bad habits or problems with truancy.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"She does not seem to have a troubled history.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Of course, at this research center, accompanying illnesses must be treated.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I wanted to ask her about her illness history when I started counseling her, but she was very shy.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I decided that I would try to get her to open up.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(80,112,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"According to her mother at home, Lain has very frightening dreams.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"They are not ordinary dreams.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"They are very realistic and almost hallucinatory.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"She visited the hospital for this reason.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Regarding the nature of the dreams, it seems that Lain doesn\'t elaborate much about their contents, but she says that she sometimes hears incomprehensible voices out of nowhere, that she is suddenly awakened and forced to watch a video.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"She sometimes plays in the park, and suddenly finds herself alone when she thought other kids were around.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"These seem to be childhood imaginary fears.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"In the future we will address these symptoms.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I hope for a recovery.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"It might be possible.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Fundamentally, even if that does not occur, she may be able to manage life at home.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"However, what her mother said that concerned me was her hallucinations.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"I will try to pinpoint the cause of these symptoms in our counseling sessions.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(81,113,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"The physical appearance of the client at the first session.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Her figure is short and thin.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"The only feature that stood out was her hairstyle.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"She has grown out the tuft of her hair on just one side of her face and tied it in a bundle.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I dont think its a popular style at school, but it seems to be her individual style.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"According to her mother, she enjoys having her hair that way.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Understanding the reason for her hairstyle may guide me in understanding her.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I will look into this in the future.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"She has a calm demeanor, and her skin is fair.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"There is otherwise nothing left to mention.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(82,114,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Although her affect is flat, she appears like any other healthy child when she smiles.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"She sometimes gets tongue-tied, but not to the point where communication with her becomes impossible.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"She seems calm and reserved.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"She understands my questions without a problem, and is capable of answering them.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"She doesnt seem to have problems with her attention span, concentration, orientation, clarity of thought, and expression of emotions, but hinders when asked about her symptoms.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(83,115,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"At this stage, I thought it would be a bad idea to ask her about her symptoms in a teasing fashion.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I was unable to find details concerning her symptoms.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"However, she generally seems to be a clever and relaxed girl.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Her mother showed me a painting she did in school.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"It was very well painted, and showed a high level of artistic sensibility.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"However, I could not find any specific points that might assist it analyzing her psychologically.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"At this stage, she appears to be at a delusional state, but there seems be a very good chance that she is a normal child.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"One point from her physical examination struck me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Her vision is excellent.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Her standard light reflex is lower than the standard range.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"However, I have not seen in her the type of dermatological or anemic problems that are common for her age.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(84,116,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Clinical notices from last session: First, concerning this case, I want to treat her as a therapist as opposed to a psychiatrist.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Therefore, I will treat Iwakura Lain as my client from now on.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"One of the reasons for this is that she is still 12 years old and is emotionally sensitive.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I do not want to make her feel that she is sick.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"In fact, from the results of her last clinical visit, the extent of what she is troubled from is nightmares and psychological damage associated with it.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Although during sessions with her, psychological discomfort can be detected, she is able to ask and answer questions without a problem.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I see no reason to advocate objections to my conclusion that she is sick, but at this point, I would like to treat her as someone without a mental illness.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"One more thing: Because I am both a psychiatrist and a counselor, my job is selecting the best position possible for my patients.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"When counseling her in the future, if I detect symptoms of mental illness, I would have to treat her as a psychiatrist.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Of course, theres a good chance that I myself will continue to treat her.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"In order to honor my research and keep it objective, I may want to ask a third party to continue to treat her clinically.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"In the meanwhile, I will continue to work with her in a research setting.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"This may be an exceptional situation at this research center, but I would like to proceed with it.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(85,117,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"The client is very cooperative and our sessions have been going smoothly.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"However, somewhere within her, she still is very cautious around me, and it is difficult to discuss her problems.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"We had some extra time, so I proposed that we play a simple game.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"She turned me down, and we went directly into our session.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"She takes much curiosity in me, an outside observer, but I think this has to do with her cautiousness around me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"She plays with dolls at home, and seems to have a complex associated with them.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"She has few friends, and playing with dolls is her way of dealing with her loneliness.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(86,118,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"In the clients response, a good understanding of language could be found.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"However, this is not related to disease.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"It displays the clients strong ability to use language.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"The client differentiated physical activity from physical education, stating that the latter is an undertaking. In school and group activities, the two can be compared quite conspicuously.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"The fact that she says she likes physical exercise but not physical education may have to do with her lack of self confidence.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(87,119,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Matters for special mention: The clients tendencies disturb me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Her light reflexes were tested at the hospital.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"She may have Adies syndrome.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Together with active auditory hallucinations and paranoia, she may have early onset general paralysis, although very unlikely.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(88,120,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Making a hasty diagnosis is taboo, but thinking of the worst, I think I should obtain cerebrospinal fluids as soon as possible.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"May I have your permission, please?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(89,121,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"My diagnosis at the hospital is affecting my client.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"She was emotionally hurt when she found out that the Rorschachs test was in fact a tool used to examine her.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"This wasnt severe to the extent of a mind-rape, but I did hurt her in our session today.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"This has made me realize that I must be discrete when bringing up the theme of disease.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I explained to her my role as a counselor, and my hopes to be helpful to her, and regained some trust from her.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I hope that in our future sessions, she will develop some goals of her own concerning counseling.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(90,122,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"She seems to be cautious about with mother.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"And as far as shes concerned, her hallucinations are real.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"She may be mistrustful of her mother because her mother does not accept that her hallucinations are real. At this point, I dont know if the hallucinations are due to some warped sense of perception, or if they are entirely imaginary.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"There are times when it is difficult to tell.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Concerning the vision the client saw floating in mid-air, they were most likely imaginary, opposed to being shapes of monsters formed by the shadows on the walls and curtains at night, etc.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Could it be that she has developed a system of sensing without perceiving?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I would like permission to examine her cerebrospinal fluid.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(91,123,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"My client has found her own diagnosis and has been studying it on her own.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"She must have a considerable amount of fear concerning her illness.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Having the label of mental illness pasted on you causes you to be stigmatized by society.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"She may need to deal with this.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I am rethinking the how the mentally ill are viewed by society.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"In our last session, I tried to eliminate her concerns about feeling that she is mentally ill. As a result, I think I was able to secure some trust in our relationship.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(92,124,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Mainly, we talked about auditory hallucinations.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"She believes that she hears voices from electric lines.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"She says that the voices she hears are not related to her.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"This could be categorized as a delusion of physical influences, but the symptoms didnt seem serious enough to be called full-blown delusions.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Her being able to hear from phone lines and electric lines seemed instead to be childlike theories.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Shes an intelligent and sensitive girl, and probably creates her own hallucinations.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"However, regarding the fact that she has hallucinations only during the day makes her very unusual.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Although I dont think my client is lying, but she says that she very rarely hallucinates while she is talking to her friends.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Most likely, references to time and place become fuzzy in her mind, and she is either confusing separate experiences, or she may have just been talking to her friends in her dreams.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(93,125,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"The relationship with my client has deteriorated.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"My own lack of consideration is to blame.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I told here that her hallucinations are an imaginary enemy.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I tried to ease her worries by being lighthearted, but this backfired and hurt my client more.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I must visit the clients home to apologize to her and give her parents a status report concerning our sessions.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(94,126,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I was somehow able to reconnect with my client.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Her symptoms havent particularly deteriorated, so I will try my best to slowly become more trustworthy.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(95,127,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I spoke to my client about her vision.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"There is a good chance that she may develop a troubling complex by comparing herself to others, thinking that she is uniquelyand abnormallyable to see and hear better than them.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"At the same time, instead of just saying that she has hyperesthesia, I believe she is dealing with the kind of dj vu that neurotic people sometimes experience.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I will exclude the details, but it seems that what she perceives comes from a poor sense of reality, and her true perceptions are abandoned.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Regarding her perception of time, if the client is telling the truth, there isnt much of a problem.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I dont know what she actually sees, or whether its due to a physical abnormality or an abnormality of perception, but as long as her underestimation of herself persists, it will be difficult to reach any fundamental solutions.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I cannot diagnose her with depersonalization neurosis just yet, but when I consider her fuzzy recollections of hallucinations, I do think she may be developing depersonalization symptoms.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(96,128,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"In order to alleviate her tendency to underestimate herself, I spoke to my client about ways to increase her self-confidence.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Her facial expression has been hard and cold, but her personality has been easy to relate to.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Because she is an intelligent client, I will have to work hard psychologically.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"But because she understands quickly, I expect that our sessions will be effective.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(97,129,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"My clients curiosities are less to do with me than they are with my profession.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Clients who inquire about the psychiatric field usually do so out of their own discomfort about their illness.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"With this client, however, her inquiries may help in her own rehabilitation.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"There is an undeniable chance that learning about her own condition may intensify her worries, but I think that can be avoided in our relationship.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(98,130,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I was able to ask my client about her hairstyle for the first time today.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Her hair looks like a good-luck charm.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I suppose she was hearing voices even with that hairstyle, but I think that she may feel that discontinuing it would cause her to have auditory hallucinations that are even worse.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"It isnt much different from the small good luck charms we put in our cars to avoid accidents.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"A person can have an overconfidence in good luck charms, of course, but I have no intention of asking her to change her hairstyle.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(99,131,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"As usual, my clients interest is entirely about psychiatry.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Although she doesnt have a complete lack of interest in everything else, she shows very little interest.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Ive grown a bit weary of her probing questions, but being a specialist, Im able to answer those questions.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I think that letting her ask will help her eliminate her lack of self-esteem, however.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Also, comparing her case to that of a similar third party client I think that she will be able to see herself more objectively by the asking and answering of questions.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(100,132,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"We are able to have completely relaxed talks now.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Ive assumed that she still has some problems having to do with memory, but she cant accept today the memories and experiences she had of herself in the past.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"From that information, I think she probably has an identity disorder and/or a disorder with self-unity.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"However, these identity problems are still in development, and theres a chance they may naturally go away as she strengthens her sense of self in therapy.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(101,133,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Communication with the client has been going satisfactorily.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"In our previous session, I was irritated by her many questions and our talk and became half-teasing.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"This definitely narrowed my relationship with her.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"In future sessions, we will focus on the growth of her sense of self and I will attempt to further establish aid to her.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(102,134,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"She has lightened up a great deal.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Much of it seems to do with a new friend shes developed in the last few months.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Additionally, she has had a change in her living arrangement, which she seems to be happy with.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Having now found a friend her own age, she will probably develop a relationship with that person that is more intimate than the one she has with me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I wonder if she still asks me questions because she doesnt know what else to talk about.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I will see how things go for the next few months, and then I would like to discontinue examinations.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(103,135,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"She wont stop pressing me with questions.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Concerning this case, it may simply be an issue with her personality.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"She still has worries about when she was hallucinating in the past when she was losing her sense of reality.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"We focused on that issue.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Her current symptoms involve excessive underestimation of herself.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"She is objectifying the adoration she has for her other self, and because her current self and her past self are completely different, it seems that she has been developing these personification symptoms on her own for some time.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"However, there is a very small chance that that will happen now.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(104,136,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"We had our talk.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"There was no problem from beginning to end.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"She is getting better.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"As far as I can see, she is just an ordinary healthy junior high schooler.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"There is no reason why she should continue to come here.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Professor Takashima, in order that I can submit my paper to the academic conference in the fall, I would like to apply to start seeing a different client.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(105,137,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Professor Takashima, regarding my request last month to see a different client, how has that progressed?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"If you could introduce me to the person in charge of the outpatients, I could arrange things from there.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(106,138,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Professor Takashima, I have prepared the final reports for my current client.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I thought that it might be a good idea to keep an appointment history, but because there seem to be have been so few problems, I did not keep one up till now.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"By next month I will prepare a final report with the appointment history.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I dont have much time until the academic conference this fall.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"May I please request this of you?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"As it is, I will not finish in time.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Are you harassing me?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(107,139,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"To the chief administrative secretary: who should I submit my report to before there is a new head of the laboratory?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(108,140,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"To the chief administrative secretary: Thank you for sending me a new client.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"The status with my current client can be found in my report.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I will send you my final report after I organize it.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"If it is not a problem, I would like to terminate the counseling of my current client.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(109,141,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"To the chief administrative secretary: In order to confirm my clients history, I spoke to one of her classmates.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I found a problem.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I am terribly sorry, but may I resume counseling this client?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(110,142,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"As I had feared, my client has created an imaginary friend, and has taken a rebellious stance toward my opinions.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"At the same time, her speech is remarkably lacking in logicality, and is almost like that of a schizophrenic.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I cannot, of course, diagnose her immediately.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Considering her loss of touch with reality in the past, her anthropomorphic symptoms, her age, and gender, she may have depersonalization neurosis.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Also, her personality disorder is extremely light, and considering her hallucinations, she may be suffering from paranoid schizophrenia.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(111,143,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"As much as possible in the future, I would like to assist her as a neutral third party, but it will be difficult because of the relationship Ive developed with her.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I would like someone else to take over her case.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Either that, or I would like to stop seeing her after our next session.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Mr. Chief Administrative Secretary, I apologize for being selfish.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I will follow through with all of my remaining work.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Please allow me to move ahead in this fashion.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(112,144,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I tried my best to repair the relationship with my client, but failed.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Somehow, after I negated the existence of her imaginary friend, shes withdrawn into her own world.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"She has become withdrawn like a patient with autism.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"We speak very little, but because she has become so distant, Im afraid there is a good chance of sending her into a panic if I speak to her carelessly.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I suppose I just need to wait and see what happens, but Im afraid that through psychotherapy, there is the danger that I may get wrapped up in her paranoid delusions.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(113,145,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"To the chief administrative secretary: Concerning future correspondences: The patient herself doesnt believe that she is very sick, and this has made therapy much more difficult.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I think the top priority should be to have her see a different therapist and allow her to find a different environment.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"However, if changing therapists is not possible, I think she would need to start a small dosage of anti-psychotic medication.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Perhaps Contom or Neoparidol might be effective.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"It may be well worth trying.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Will I need to submit a request to the overseeing authorities for this?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(114,146,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"The client had a pleasant demeanor in our session from beginning to end.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Perhaps there was no need to do anything abruptly.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"The client hasnt changed her feelings about me from the past, and our casual conversations go well as long as I avoid talking about her imaginary friend.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"What bothers me, though, are the prying personal questions asks.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I sometimes think that she means to intentionally work me up.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"But that may just be due to my impatience.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Somehow I want to have an intimate relationship with her again.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I want to gradually redevelop objectivity and lead our sessions.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(115,147,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"The client has changed so much that she doesnt seem to be the same person anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Is that true, or am I being subjective?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Could something have changed due to the progression of her symptoms?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"As we talked, she made remarks that I couldn\'t understand.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"She also made some inciteful remarks.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"During our session, I forgot myself and became hysterical.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I cant handle it anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I can do no more.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Please have someone else take charge of this case.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(116,148,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Overall, she doesnt seem very youthful.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"She appears older than her age.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Even when we talk at a relaxed tone, she moves her eyes about irratically.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"She also moves her wrists about oddly, and appears anxious.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"She probably is very conscious about her bodily sensations, and doesnt admit to being ill because of her pride.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"She blames what is happening to her on fatigue and lack of sleep.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(117,149,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"During our talk, she said that she couldnt imagine herself being happy.\", \"actor\": \"Toko and Lain together (Lain can only be heard joining at the end)\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"She said that she has no hope for her future.\", \"actor\": \"Toko and Lain together (Lain can only be heard joining at the end)\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"She has lost her sense of confidence, and has slipped into a pessimistic mood.\", \"actor\": \"Toko and Lain together (Lain can only be heard joining at the end)\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"She would go into hysterics if stimulated.\", \"actor\": \"Toko and Lain together (Lain can only be heard joining at the end)\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"The client is scrupulous and diligent.\", \"actor\": \"Toko and Lain together (Lain can only be heard joining at the end)\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"She has anxiety about having harmonious interpersonal relationships.\", \"actor\": \"Toko and Lain together (Lain can only be heard joining at the end)\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"She is transformational and melancholy.\", \"actor\": \"Toko and Lain together (Lain can only be heard joining at the end)\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"From now on, I will continue trying to relieve her psychological burdens and to provide her guidance.\", \"actor\": \"Toko and Lain together (Lain can only be heard joining at the end)\"}]'),(118,150,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"The client accidentally poured scalding water on her hand during our session.\", \"actor\": \"Toko and Lain together\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"She went about cleaning up afterwards as if nothing had happened.\", \"actor\": \"Toko and Lain together\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"There is a chance that there is something wrong with her brain organically.\", \"actor\": \"Toko and Lain together\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"We may need to perform CT scans and some other tests to determine if this is so.\", \"actor\": \"Toko and Lain together\"}]'),(119,151,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"My client is not opening up to me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko and Lain together\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Some kind of drastic treatment may be necessary.\", \"actor\": \"Toko and Lain together\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"When I intentionally rubbed her the wrong way, she showed her combative side.\", \"actor\": \"Toko and Lain together\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I think that in the future, lowering of mental efficiency, deterioration of memory, and deterioration of healing will take place, and an inferiority complex with self-reproach will take over.\", \"actor\": \"Toko and Lain together\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"As a result, impulsive behavior will come about, among other symptoms.\", \"actor\": \"Toko and Lain together\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"There is a good chance that her sense of reality will be troubling to her.\", \"actor\": \"Toko and Lain together\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"She may want to commit suicide.\", \"actor\": \"Toko and Lain together\"}]'),(120,152,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Her personality speedily continues to decline.\", \"actor\": \"Toko and Lain together\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Her emotions are flattened.\", \"actor\": \"Toko and Lain together\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"She is indifferent and lethargic.\", \"actor\": \"Toko and Lain together\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"She doesnt show a feminine demeanor as she used to.\", \"actor\": \"Toko and Lain together\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Until now, Ive always served tea for visitors, but I didnt get around to it today.\", \"actor\": \"Toko and Lain together\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"The person one imagines oneself to be and that persons difference in ability compared to herThe clients ego is collapsing.\", \"actor\": \"Toko and Lain together\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Even in my presence, she exposes lack of confidence and appears sick.\", \"actor\": \"Toko and Lain together\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Sometimes, I dont know about me\", \"actor\": \"Toko and Lain together\"}]'),(121,153,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Her responses to my questions have become sluggish.\", \"actor\": \"Toko and Lain together\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Her lack of self-confidence seems to be altering her self-assessment.\", \"actor\": \"Toko and Lain together\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Her intellect is affected.\", \"actor\": \"Toko and Lain together\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"The assessment of her character has not taken place. She has completely lost sense of herself.\", \"actor\": \"Toko and Lain together\"}]'),(122,154,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Patients with melancholia, it is good to treat them right at the onset of the disease.\", \"actor\": \"Toko and Lain together\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"In addition to the neurosis, symptoms of depression and schizophrenia can be seen.\", \"actor\": \"Toko and Lain together\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"She may have atypical psychosis.\", \"actor\": \"Toko and Lain together\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Her brainwaves should be tested at the hospital, along with some other tests.\", \"actor\": \"Toko and Lain together\"}]'),(123,155,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"She doesnt understand what I am saying.\", \"actor\": \"Toko and Lain together\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"She responds to technical psychiatric language, but not to ordinary speech.\", \"actor\": \"Toko and Lain together\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Ive decided to diagnose her with verbal auditory agnosia.\", \"actor\": \"Toko and Lain together\"}]'),(124,156,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"The client has an indirect reason for going to the trouble of surrounding herself with love.\", \"actor\": \"Toko and Lain together\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Using a continuous approach, I think I can regain her psyche.\", \"actor\": \"Toko and Lain together\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I will discontinue medicating her, and resume psychotherapy and milieu therapy.\", \"actor\": \"Toko and Lain together\"}]'),(125,157,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"The client has discovered the connection between herself and reality, and has completely recovered from her ego disturbance.\", \"actor\": \"Toko and Lain together\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"The results from the PPRS and HMB tests showed no problems whatsoever.\", \"actor\": \"Toko and Lain together\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I completed my first treatment successfully.\", \"actor\": \"Toko and Lain together\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Thank you, my valuable client.\", \"actor\": \"Lain alone\"}]'),(126,158,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"February 7th. Interview for testimony from a witness to the suicide of a high school girl.\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Before we begin with questions, Id like to confirm your identity.\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Shinji Makino 29 years old.\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Office worker.\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Is that correct?\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Could you remind me of your address?\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Sure. Shinagawa ward, Kamiosaki, 30-19-105, Meguro-residence 504.\", \"actor\": \"Shinji\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Thank you.\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"This interview will be recorded, by the way, but it will be kept confidential, so please dont worry.\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Alright.\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Lets get started.\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Could you tell me what you saw at the scene of the suicide in as much detail as possible?\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"Where do you want me to start? From the morning of that day?\", \"actor\": \"Shinji\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"No. Just what you remember from around the time of the suicide. Relax. Dont feel pressured.\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"Uhh.\", \"actor\": \"Shinji\"}]'),(127,159,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"You were there as a twosome.\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Yeah. So?\", \"actor\": \"Shinji\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Well, according to a storekeeper who saw you, the girl you were with was very young.\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Yeah. And?\", \"actor\": \"Shinji\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Well, you see, prostitution takes place at that store.\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Sorry to tell you, but I dont have any hobbies like that. Shes just a girl I knew.\", \"actor\": \"Shinji\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Is that right? Well, Id also like to ask her a few questions too.\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I havent had any contact with her, and why do I have to do all this for you anyway?\", \"actor\": \"Shinji\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Because wed like to have as much information as we can to understand why a high school student is dead.\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"We havent even been able to retrieve the gun used in the crime.\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"And you think she took it with her? Youve got to be kidding. Shes in junior high school!\", \"actor\": \"Shinji\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Were not certain, were just not ruling out the possibility.\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"Among the people at that store at that time, the only person who we havent been able to identify is the girl you were with.\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"Could you help us out with more detailed information?\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}]'),(128,160,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I don\'t want to talk if my testimony is going to harm her.\", \"actor\": \"Shinji\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"No, nothing has been decided yet.\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Wed just like to be able to contact her.\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Theres nothing for you to worry about.\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"But is there something\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"No, nothing.\", \"actor\": \"Shinji\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I did meet her through the Internet.\", \"actor\": \"Shinji\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"But she wasnt the kind of kid that would reveal an e-mail address.\", \"actor\": \"Shinji\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"She was good at computers.\", \"actor\": \"Shinji\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"What do you mean?\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"She tapped into computers.\", \"actor\": \"Shinji\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"You mean she was a hacker?\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"No doubt about it.\", \"actor\": \"Shinji\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"Then you wouldnt be able to contact her?\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"I dont mean that I couldnt.\", \"actor\": \"Shinji\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"I reached her once.\", \"actor\": \"Shinji\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"But I cant guarantee that she still even has that address.\", \"actor\": \"Shinji\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"I see.\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"Then theres little we can do.\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"Well handle it from here, then.\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"Could you give us her address?\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 21, \"text\": \"Sure, I dont mind.\", \"actor\": \"Shinji\"}, {\"line\": 22, \"text\": \"If you dont have it, we can have some of our specialists look into it.\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 23, \"text\": \"If you do hear from her, could you keep our little meeting here a secret?\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 24, \"text\": \"It would be important for you, too, that you keep this a secret.\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 25, \"text\": \"Is that a threat?\", \"actor\": \"Shinji\"}, {\"line\": 26, \"text\": \"Oh, not at all.\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 27, \"text\": \"We have better things to do than make threats.\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 28, \"text\": \"As long as we arent interfered with, things will be just fine.\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 29, \"text\": \"Thats what I mean.\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}]'),(129,161,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Hello, Makino-san.\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Its been a while.\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"You dont seem to be doing very well, so Ill keep this short.\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Can you take responsibility for the things you say to us from now on?\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Makino-san?\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I havent been able to sleep. I feel better when Im looking at the computer.\", \"actor\": \"Shinji\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Smoking isnt really allowed here, but if it relaxes you, go ahead.\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Lets begin.\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"The reason youre here\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Its about Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Shinji\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Yes it is. Did you meet her after the shooting?\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Probably.\", \"actor\": \"Shinji\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"Probably?\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"I dont know anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Shinji\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"Detective, could you contact a psychiatrist for me?\", \"actor\": \"Shinji\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"I cant take it anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Shinji\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"I dont want to die, but all of a sudden, I want to die now!\", \"actor\": \"Shinji\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"Look at these scars!\", \"actor\": \"Shinji\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"Theres nowhere left to cut!\", \"actor\": \"Shinji\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"This is interrogation room number 7.\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"Bring a doctor here quickly.\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 21, \"text\": \"This ones no good, either.\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 22, \"text\": \"Hey, cut it out!\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 23, \"text\": \"Sorry.\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 24, \"text\": \"Forget about the doctor.\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 25, \"text\": \"Bring a cleaner.\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}, {\"line\": 26, \"text\": \"And a cup of coffee, too.\", \"actor\": \"Cop\"}]'),(130,162,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"First of all, regarding the suicides of two researchers at our center, there have been rumors that their deaths had to do with them exploring some strange area of research, like something out of a science fiction novel.\", \"actor\": \"Research center representative\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I reassure you that that is completely untrue.\", \"actor\": \"Research center representative\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"This center specializes in the study of communication and mental illness.\", \"actor\": \"Research center representative\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Fundamentally, this is not a facility for clinical medicine.\", \"actor\": \"Research center representative\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Our staff sometimes visits hospitals at their invitation, but basically, all we do here is research.\", \"actor\": \"Research center representative\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I dont know how to apologize to her parents of those researchers.\", \"actor\": \"Research center representative\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I am quite overcome.\", \"actor\": \"Research center representative\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Ive heard that the female researcher who took her life had some patients.\", \"actor\": \"Reporter\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"She was unique.\", \"actor\": \"Representative\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"She treated people clinically at this research center.\", \"actor\": \"Representative\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"But this was her own decision.\", \"actor\": \"Representative\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Ive heard rumors that one of the researchers who died was mentally ill. Is that true?\", \"actor\": \"Reporter\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"We cant really comment on that right now.\", \"actor\": \"Representative\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"But seeing that she took her own life, she may have had some type of mental illness.\", \"actor\": \"Representative\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"There are many things a person may call it, but theres no doubt that she was suffering deeply.\", \"actor\": \"Representative\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"Suicide is very extreme, but she must have been under a lot of stress.\", \"actor\": \"Representative\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"A psychiatrist is still just a human being.\", \"actor\": \"Representative\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"Did she catch her mental illness from her patients?\", \"actor\": \"Reporter\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"Mental illness isnt a contagious disease, So no, she didnt catch anything from her patients.\", \"actor\": \"Representative\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"We wouldnt use that expression.\", \"actor\": \"Representative\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"She may have been influenced by the patients to a degree.\", \"actor\": \"Representative\"}, {\"line\": 21, \"text\": \"You may call that a sort of contagion if youd like.\", \"actor\": \"Representative\"}, {\"line\": 22, \"text\": \"Its a matter of semantics.\", \"actor\": \"Representative\"}, {\"line\": 23, \"text\": \"But dont let anyone trick you about this sort of thing.\", \"actor\": \"Representative\"}, {\"line\": 24, \"text\": \"All of this doctors patients were healthy.\", \"actor\": \"Representative\"}, {\"line\": 25, \"text\": \"I cant get into specifics because of privacy issues.\", \"actor\": \"Representative\"}, {\"line\": 26, \"text\": \"Are there other things that might explain her behavior?\", \"actor\": \"Reporter\"}, {\"line\": 27, \"text\": \"Did the researcher who took her life may have had devious intentions?\", \"actor\": \"Reporter\"}, {\"line\": 28, \"text\": \"Were in the middle of an investigation, and I cant comment too much on that out of respect for her friends and family.\", \"actor\": \"Representative\"}, {\"line\": 29, \"text\": \"However, Ive been informed that that has absolutely nothing to do with it.\", \"actor\": \"Representative\"}, {\"line\": 30, \"text\": \"I would rather\", \"actor\": \"Representative\"}, {\"line\": 31, \"text\": \"You would rather?\", \"actor\": \"Reporter\"}, {\"line\": 32, \"text\": \"Anyway, Ive heard that that has nothing to do with it.\", \"actor\": \"Representative\"}, {\"line\": 33, \"text\": \"Ill say this for our researchers that they are very fine human beings that are very seriously committed about what they do.\", \"actor\": \"Representative\"}, {\"line\": 34, \"text\": \"What was the likelihood of this kind of thing happening?\", \"actor\": \"Reporter\"}, {\"line\": 35, \"text\": \"Well, it may have been less likely if we had caught it earlier.\", \"actor\": \"Representative\"}, {\"line\": 36, \"text\": \"On the other hand, we may have not paid enough attention because our researchers really have it together and are professional and hardworking.\", \"actor\": \"Representative\"}, {\"line\": 37, \"text\": \"We would like to help avoid this is the future by making psychological assessments of our staff.\", \"actor\": \"Representative\"}]'),(131,163,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Hey, why dont you walk home with me? Lets hang out on the way there!\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Sure if you want to\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I want to buy lipstick!\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Teacher will scold you for using lipstick again\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Lain you are too stiff. Lets both use it! I think it will look good on you.\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"No Its needless for me. Its no use for me to try to be cute.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"You should have confidence in yourself! I think you are cute! So come shopping with me.\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Ok\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(132,164,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Lain, do you have a crush on anyone?\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"No not really\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"How about you?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I love Nakahara in Class 3. He looks cool.\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I will try to get along with him.\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I hope it works out\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(133,165,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"What do you do to kill time?\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Cleaning?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Oh, youre tidy.\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I have a trouble because I have many unnecessary things in my room.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Yeah, my room is like that. I often go impulse shopping, so I have lots of lipstick I dont use.\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"How about trading makeup and accessories?\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"But Lain, you dont use makeup.\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Are you using the lipstick we bought together?\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"No\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"You should use a little makeup. I think it suits you!\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}]'),(134,166,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I hope something great will happen like in a movie.\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Many people will get killed, but I dont die.\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"And I resolve it with a very cool detective.\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"For that, Ill be a big star!!!\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Sorry Im saying such strange things.\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Hey, dont look at me with such cold eyes\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"My eyes are always like this\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"What? Are you trying to make me laugh?\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Did I fail?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Aha, ha, ha, yes, you failed!\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Its just like you to say something like that.\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}]'),(135,167,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Hey, Lain. Do you think that youre a special person?\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Special?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Everyone says, Lain is not a normal girl and Isnt she dangerous?\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Ive known you since we were children, so I say to them No, she is normal.\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Also, Im a little similar to you.\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"It makes me sad that Im not special like other people!\", \"ac