t\": \"So youre a private tutor.\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"People like you are rare nowadays, arent you?\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"You get this involved about your students?\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Enough to ask other kids about them?\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Ive been a bit distracted and out of focus lately, and I was concerned that that might have been rubbing off on Lain and that I havent been teaching her properly.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Either that, or maybe things havent been going well for her at school.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I think shes doing ok.\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"From your point of view, is she doing well in school?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"I don\'t really know.\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"We used to be friends, but since we entered junior high school, we havent talked to each other that much.\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"Is this a test to see if shes been behaving herself?\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"I dont know what other kids are doing outside of school.\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"Wouldnt you get your answers more quickly by consulting an advisor at school or something?\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"Oh, no, no.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"Its nothing serious like that.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"Not at all.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"But shes a calm girl, isnt she?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 21, \"text\": \"She doesnt open up so easily?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 22, \"text\": \"I was just curious about how shes doing in school.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 23, \"text\": \"Hmm.\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 24, \"text\": \"Well, I have nothing to lose by talking to you, so ask me whatever you want.\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 25, \"text\": \"I havent talked to Lain much recently.\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 26, \"text\": \"She doesnt have that many friends.\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 27, \"text\": \"She used to be a little somber.\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 28, \"text\": \"I guess you could say that shes become more somber lately.\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}]'),(148,180,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"We were in the same class in 5th and 6th grade.\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"We were in the same group because we sat close to each other.\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"She was quiet, so she didnt talk to many people other than me.\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"She seemed like a sister to me.\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"We didnt play together much, though.\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"When would you say that Lain started to change?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"She wasnt so somber until about a year ago.\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"When I see her these days, we dont have much to say.\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Its too bad, but lately, shes just another classmate to me.\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Have you talked to her at all recently?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Recently? I seem to remember something. What was it, I wonder.\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Can you remember?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"How weird. I usually have a good memory.\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"Do you remember talking about shopping or boys?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"No. I dont think we talked about that.\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}]'),(149,181,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"What was it?\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Something about my memory.\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I remember now.\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I remember that we were in biology class.\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Lain was asking the teacher after class about the brain and how memories are stored.\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I thought that that was pretty impressive.\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I asked her what she had asked the teacher, and she said she asked the teacher how to recollect memories.\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Weird.\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}]'),(150,182,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I dont dislike Lain. But lately shes been hard to approach.\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I know what you mean.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Dont you, though?\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I think a lot of the kids see her that way.\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"No one is bullying her, now, but most of us are pretty indifferent to her.\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Yeah.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"You ought to talk to her. Tell her to laugh the way she used to.\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"The way she used to?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"In the old memories I have of her, she was always smiling.\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"I remember that when we were together, she would always laugh.\", \"actor\": \"Kyoko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I see. I sort of had that impression. Thats why I was concerned.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(151,183,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Yes. are you a friend of Misato-chan, Kyoko?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Whos Misa