": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"It wouldnt have been like this if I had kept my mouth closed.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Even when I apologized, she said, why do I have to apologize to you? She doesnt like me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"She really doesnt like me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(185,217,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I have nothing to write in my diary today.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(186,218,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Toko-san is a big jerk.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(187,219,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I cant believe what Toko-san said.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Nothing will return to the way it used to be.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Im disliked.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Toko-san said to keep writing in my diary.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I dont need a diary.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I dont have anything to write.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Nothing has changed.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I just go to school everyday as usual.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Im alone during recess and lunchtime, and no one talks to me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(188,220,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"How mean.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Writing graffiti on my desk.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"As usual, Kyoko-chan wont say anything to me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I didnt do that.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Ive never gone out with Tomo-kun.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I felt like everyone was mocking me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I dont want to go to school anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(189,221,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Kamiya sensei came to my house and talked with my Mom.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Mom looked frustrated.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Kamiya sensei said that if I skip class any more, I wouldnt be able to graduate.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Mom and Dad were talking about it after dinner.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Mom was crying and Dad looked very distressed.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Am I a bad kid?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I want to disappear.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(190,222,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Today Dad skipped work and talked with me all day.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Hes a kind Dad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I wonder if Ill make friends if I went to a different school.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I wonder if school will be fun somewhere else.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I wonder if I can go to the school Tomo-kun goes to.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(191,223,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"My teacher visited our house again today.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"It seems that I can go to junior high school.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Mom bowed to the teacher many times.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Im sorry, Mom.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"If I go to junior high school, I wont cause trouble anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(192,224,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"When I went to school today, Kamiya-sensei said that I would graduate, and that I dont have to force myself to come to school.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Does he not want me to be at school?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Is he letting me graduate because he doesnt want to see me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"To get rid of me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Im never going to that school again.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(193,225,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Is there a meaning to why Im here? Does someone need me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(194,226,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I named a special gift Dad got for me today.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I named it Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Shes another me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"My only friend.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"But when I go to junior high, Ill make real friends.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"If I appear at ease and lighthearted, wont other kids like me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(195,227,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I talked to Dad about computer connections.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"He went through a lot of elaborate steps to set up my computer.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"We worked hard for about 5 hours setting it up.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Dad was reading lots of books about computers while we did it.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Once we were done, Dad called Mom, and the three of us were delighted.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I dont think we felt so good together as a family in a long time.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"It seems like since I stopped going to school, Mom and Dad havent been as happy as they used to be.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Im sorry.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(196,228,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Computer networks are amazing.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"No one can see my face from there, and I dont feel embarrassed.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I feel like Im becoming a different me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"There are so many people online, and theyre kind to me even though Im just someone with a lot of problems.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Im so happy that people could be so kind to me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(197,229,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I surfed the net all day again today.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Im surprised at what an easy-going person I can be on the net.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"My name on the net is Lain, but it seems that they cant tell from that that Im a girl.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"If something interesting happens, I get e-mails telling me about it right away.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Everybody is friendly.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"No one can bully me here.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"My eyes hurt after I stare at the monitor all day long.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"But for me, having my eyesight deteriorate would be a good thing.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(198,230,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Programs seemed difficult at first, but some of them got easier after I studied them.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I have time now anyway, so I think Ill study.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"It shouldnt be any trouble.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Mom and Dad wont be there to protect me forever.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Ill borrow a book from the library tomorrow.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I can study when Im online, but if Im online all the time, I might not be able to receive phone calls.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(199,231,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Maybe Kyoko-chan is worried about me. Wellprobably not.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(200,232,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I started a game on the net.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Its called the Mouse Game You sell tickets to your friends and make money.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"But if I start making lots of money, the other players will have a grudge against me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"There will be people who want to kill me then, so I have to be careful.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"At first I thought this was just a game, but it made me feel bad after a while, and I wanted to cry.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"There was a questionnaire that came with the game asking me what I thought of it, so I wrote the company telling them what I honestly thought.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I guess they know who I am now and dont like me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Im sad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I dont like games like that.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Id rather play a game that everyone can laugh with and enjoy together.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"It isnt for me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(201,233,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"It was a graduation ceremony, but I didn\'t want to go.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Once Im in junior high, Ill go for sure.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I promise.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I wont worry Mom anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"You took my clothes to the dry cleaners, didnt you, Mom?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Im sorry.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(202,234,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"What does everyone think about me? Does anyone think anything about me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(203,235,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Spring break starts today.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I havent been going to school, though.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"When I was at the library reading a book about UNIX, a guy next to me who looked about the age of a college student gave me a really weird look.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Studying computers is tough because there are many technical terms and difficult kanji, but I enjoy this.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Theres nothing painful about it, and its more fun than grammar or math.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I understand English better now, and I understand things better in general, but there are still many things I dont understand.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I think Ill ask Dad about some of this stuff.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I wonder if Dad will give me a weird look like the guy in the library.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(204,236,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"When I decoded a file that came today by e-mail, I saw the image of a dead infant.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I couldnt find the address the file came from.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I wonder if its from the person that started that tasteless online game.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Im getting scared to open my mail now.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I cant leave here, though.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"At least not until I enter junior high and start an ordinary life.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"When I start junior high, and Ill have friends and Ill be busy, and I might not have time to come to the net.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I ought to study the net now while I still have time.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(205,237,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I was sad during dinner today.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Dad said that he has to go overseas because of work.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"It was so sudden I was surprised and speechless.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"He said hed be away for 2 months.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I started to cry all of a sudden, and I lost my appetite.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Dad looked worried, and he hugged me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Well go to see him off at the airport tomorrow.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(206,238,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Dads work seems to be really difficult.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I want to work when I grow up.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I want to be like Dad and live with self-confidence.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(207,239,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Well saw Dad off today.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Mom seemed really sad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"We waved good-bye to each other for a long time as he took the escalator to the gate.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"On the way home, Mom took me to a restaurant.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"It was a nice dinner, but it was sad knowing that it will just be me and Mom at the dinner table for a long time.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Im sure Mom feels sad, too.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"God, please let Dad come home safely.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(208,240,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Mom, do you feel uneasy with me? I know Im odd. Its ok. I wont bother you.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(209,241,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"When I told my net buddies about that gross e-mail with the dead baby, they said there might be a way to trace it.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Its not something Im supposed to do, but I feel like a detective, and its a bit fun.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Whoever sent that e-mail is at fault, anyway.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I can retaliate a little.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Im not such a good person anyway.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"What can I do if people say that there is something wrong with my character?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"After all, theres something wrong with me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Strange is what I am?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Im strange, arent I, Mr. Rabbit?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(210,242,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"By following instructions I learned yesterday, I was able to access the host site.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"It was easy.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Maybe Im a genius at this kind of thing.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I found some footprints when I did some downloading.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Im figuring out how to trace down that sick person.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Im going to mail him to set a trap for him.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I cant forgive someone who does something like that.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Im not going to cry myself to sleep anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(211,243,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Ill solve it with my own strength. My own strength. I should be able to do that now.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(212,244,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"That was it after all!\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Within 2 hours of mailing that guy, I got a response.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I was curious what it was, but I was sure it would be gross, so I didnt.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I decoded it, set a trap, and encoded it.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"This way, that person will never do this again.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(213,245,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I took the information on his host site and spread it publicly on a mirror-site. I didnt look at any of the pictures because theyd all be gross.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"The text of his site was gross, too.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Im starting to worry if I trapped the right person.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"What if I got the wrong persons data or identificationI dont want to ever do this again.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"It feels good to be able to do things others cant do.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Is there something wrong with me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(214,246,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Its horrible, but I cant do anything about it.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Someones been reading my diary.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Its been copied and displayed on an FTP site with a vulgar title.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I stopped it, but over 20 people have already read it.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Why did this all happen?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Other people can do what I can do.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I think Ill avoid the net for a while.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I want to see whats going on, but my diary might be on someones site, being reproduced right now.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I know.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Im going to send an information-deleting engine into the net.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"But what if whoever took my diary has the diarys back-up information, too?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Im sure the person who took my diary is that gross guy.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"And if its him, he would certainly have that information.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"Im so mad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"I cant win this by myself.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"So this is what I amount to.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"I think Ill consult Mr. Rabbit.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"I wonder what will help.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(215,247,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Are the people who enjoy doing horrible things and hurting people really human beings like me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"But what am I?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(216,248,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I dont understand anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Did that strange person know Mr. Rabbit?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"He said, Leave it to me, and forget about it. Oh, Im mad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I want revenge.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Im not going to cry myself to sleep.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I want to forget everything I want to forget.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"The things I dont like.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"The me I dont like.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Can I do something magical like that?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(217,249,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"School will start soon.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Im going to be different this time for sure.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Im going to be an ordinary, light-hearted junior high school student.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I hope I dont have many of the same classmates I had in elementary school.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Mom and Dad were talking on the phone.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Were they worried about me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Thats ok. You can both relax and not worry.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I saw it again for the first time in a long while.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Is it an illusion?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Is there something wrong with my mind?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I dont care if Im sick or not.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"I just want it to stop.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(218,250,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I started bleeding when I was brushing my teeth.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Could it be pyorrhea?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"My teeth were always so healthy.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I can taste my blood.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Its a bit bitter and I dont like it.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I think I wont stop bleeding and that I wont be able to fall asleep.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Is it because Im uneasy about starting junior high school tomorrow?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(219,251,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Im different. Im a different me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(220,252,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Mom came to the ceremony for the start of the school year.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"None of the kids from grade school were in my class.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I was relieved.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"The teacher in charge was a nice person, and I made some friends.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I was assigned to a seat.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Theres a different feel here compared to grade school.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I cant hang out with most of the kids, but I think Ill get along with just one of the girls sitting next to me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Shes quiet, but thats the kind of person thats easy for me to be around.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Its great to meet you, Misato-chan!\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(221,253,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I feel like everything will go great now.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"As long as I have one friend, Im ok. Dad, I hope you come home soon!\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(222,254,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Today I did a lot of things with Misato-chan.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Shes good at physical education, though Im not.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I think Im more into liberal arts.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Misato-chan has been playing the violin since she was very young.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Shes even been in competitions.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Shes amazing.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Shes good with computers, too.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I didnt tell her that Im into computers, though.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I wanted to keep things having to do with me and the net a secret.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"On the net, I can be the sort of me that isnt so careful.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(223,255,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I told Toko-san all about it.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I talked about Misato-chan through the whole session.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Toko-san said, youre doing really well, and I was a bit embarrassed.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I wonder what Toko-san did for her extracurricular activities.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I think shes good at physical education.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"She said that she went to America for school.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Maybe things are different there.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(224,256,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Misato-chan said that she wanted to be in same extracurricular class with me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Im nowhere as good as her in music, and she said that she didnt want to be in music class with me anyway.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"The people in the joint research group were very nice, but I wasn\'t sure if I wanted to join.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I thought I would join an art class.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Ive always enjoyed drawing.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(225,257,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Misato-chan is really good to me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Were always together.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Im sad when she doesnt come to school.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I wish I had more friends.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I wonder if Im being selfish.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Am I greedy?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I wonder if Misato-chan is ok when she is alone.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"If I skip school tomorrow, how would she feel?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"If I tried something like that, though, she wont like me anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(226,258,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I didnt want to stay home from school deliberately.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"My head hurt, and I saw that thing again, so I stayed home.\", 