elf to do too much? Im not, am I?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(229,261,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I drew a picture of Toko-san and went to her office to show her, but one of the people there said that she was out.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I guess shes really busy.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Dad is going to come back soon, and Ive been feeling good lately.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I cant see that anymore, so I think Ill go back to the Net for old times sake.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I havent seen Mr. Rabbit in a while.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I have to say thanks for that time.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I look pretty good when Im making progress.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(230,262,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Im not forcing myself to laugh. This is me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(231,263,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I saw that on the Net.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I havent had a problem with that before.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Why is it happening?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"But I dont have to go to the Net anyway.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Ive written a letter to Mr. Rabbit, so I wont go back to the Net for a while.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Things are going well anyway.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Its ok, Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Im not alone anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(232,264,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Dad came home.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I talked to him a lot.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"About me, about drawing, about Misato-chan.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I talked and talked and talked until Mom said that Dad is tired and that I