 \"Any way, Im glad that shes better.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Ill take her the gift I couldnt give her yesterday.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I skipped extracurricular activities and went to an ice cream shop with Misato-chan instead.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Its always fun to be around Misato-chan.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Im glad shes better.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(241,273,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"This is the same as always. Nothing will change. Im fine just like this.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(242,274,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"When I was checking e-mails to see if anything came from Mr. Rabbit, I found a weird e-mail.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"This time it was a picture of a dead, naked woman, tied up with ropes.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Strangely, it said that the e-mail came from Mr. Rabbit.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Mr. Rabbit wouldnt do something like that.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Its that guy again.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Ill let Mr. Rabbit know.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I cant believe this.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Why would someone do this?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Im scared to check my e-mail now.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Id like to check my e-mails, but if I access the Net and I see that againI was getting better.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Im not sick.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(243,275,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Right, I\'m really not sick.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"What Touko-san is saying since she said it, it can\'t be wrong, right?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I should believe her.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(244,276,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I have to do a drawing for a cultural festival soon.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I wonder what to draw.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Im not sure.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"One of the leaders said that it can be something simple.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I wonder what.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"A drawing of Bike-chan?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Misato-chan?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Dad, Mom?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Toko-san?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Myself?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Its difficult to draw people.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"If the drawing doesnt look like the person, its embarrassing.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(245,277,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"What is Misato-chan going to draw? Lain? Or someone I dont know?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(246,278,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Misato-chan said that she draws with her computer.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Maybe Ill try that, too.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Ill ask her how to do it.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(247,279,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Software is expensive.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"A digitizing tablet seems necessary.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"It seems that its better if there is a scanner.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Its difficult with machinery these days.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I cant afford this stuff with my allowance.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I wonder if Misato-chans family is rich.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Ill talk to Dad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"If 