 \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Too bad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Misato-chan is good-looking and smart.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"She could get a boy.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Maybe she doesnt want one.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"She looked really bothered.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Maybe she already has a boyfriend that I dont know anything about.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"Thats sad, too.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(251,283,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Its impossible to know everything, isnt it?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Im not Misato-chan.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"But if I was the person I used to be, I might have been that way, too.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(252,284,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I asked Misato-chan if she was going out with someone.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"She laughed.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Well, after all, were together all the time.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"When I was changing clothes for gym class, I noticed that Misato-chan had big breasts.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"My chest is flat.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Im jealous.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"But I dont have that yet either.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"All the others are really becoming girls.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I think Im moving slower than everybody else.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(253,285,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"The body doesn\'t matter much.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"What matters is the heart.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"If my heart is perturbed, no one will like me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(254,286,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I went to see Toko-san today.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"When I asked her how much longer we should meet each other, she looked troubled.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"She said that I could come over with the idea of enjoying myself instead of thinking of our meetings as therapy, but I didnt want to have to explain myself to Misato-chan.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I wonder what Misato-chan is thinking.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I dont want to keep any secrets from her, but Im afraid to tell her the truth.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(255,287,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"You\'re busy with your own work, aren\'t you, Toko-san?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(256,288,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Misato-chan gave me a present.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"She said it was to repay me for the gift I gave her.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Misato-chans present was a CD of her playing a violin.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"She plays beautifully.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Listening to her play is like drifting off into a dream.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"She can really play.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"She blushed a little when she gave me her CD.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"That was a bit unlike her, and it was cute.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I guess Misato-chan makes expressions like that, too.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"It seems like there is more of the Misato-chan that only I know.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"When I played the CD for Mom, she didn\'t seem too interested.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Maybe she doesnt like the violin.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(257,289,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"We got a new PC today.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"It looks very expensive.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Its small and round, but its very fast.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Its different from the computers weve had before, but the man said that the applications are similar, so there shouldnt be many problems.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I feel important all of a sudden, and happy.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Thank you, Dad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"When I grow up, I wonder if I will find work related to managing information or something.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Ive been studying hard and want to make myself useful.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Still, I dont want a job that only has to do with machines.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(258,290,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Misato-chan came to visit my house today.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Mom seemed to be in a good moodsort of.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Misato-chan taught me how to draw.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Mom came and checked in on us often.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Dad, Mom, Misato-chan and I had dinner together.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"It was great.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I didnt learn that much about drawing, but Misato-chan said that she will visit again soon.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"We took Misato-chan back to home in Dads car.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"She has a very fancy house in a rich neighborhood.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"It was almost dreamlike.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Misato-chans mom came to the door and spoke with Dad a bit.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"She was really pretty, like an actress.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"I guess that a pretty girls like Misato-chan must come from beautiful mothers like that.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"But only a girl like me could come from my kind of Mom.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"Im sorry, Mom.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"But I really had fun today.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(259,291,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I guess were different from birth.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"But if I was born there, wouldnt I have been pretty like Misato-chan?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(260,292,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I drew a picture and submitted it to the cultural fair, but I dont think I have much talent.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Compared to everyone else, Im not very good.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Misato-chan does great.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"She said that she was still mid-process with her work, but I thought it was great already anyway.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"She drew a picture of Pegasus, with deep blue skies.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"It looked as though Pegasus was really flying.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I dont think I could draw a Pegasus that looks like it is flying.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I think Ill just draw what I feel like drawing.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Id rather draw pictures of Misato-chan more than anything else, but maybe she wont like that.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(261,293,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Im a little envious of Misato-chan.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"She can do so many things.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Other than using the Net, theres nothing I can do better than Misato-chan.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(262,294,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I tried to remember Misato-chans face and drew it.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I wonder if it looks much like her.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I showed it to Mom, who didnt have much to say.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Dad said it was good, but Im still not very confident.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I think Ill quit the cultural fair.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Today there was something about the new Navi that I didnt understand, so I went and bought a book again.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"There arent many books about this kind of computer, so I didnt have much to choose from, but I bought a book that has to do with command lists.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Its based in UNIX, so much of it was familiar, but it helped me understand assembly, which I had trouble with.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I connected two computers so that they could exchange files, and called it a day.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(263,295,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I saw an accident on my way home today.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Something fell at a construction site and someone died.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Cop cars and ambulances were everywhere, and lots of people, too.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Its sad that someone died.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I wouldnt want something like that to happen to me all of a sudden.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I am\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(264,296,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I finished my artwork of Misato-chan.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"It was very popular in class.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Its very pretty and artful.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I bet it will stand out and draw attention at the culture fair.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I used pastels and watercolors.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Misato-chan said that I did a good job, but I wonder if I really ought to have done a painting of her.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I feel that I havent expressed myself as much as I wanted in my painting.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"What kind of painting should I do?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Misato-chans paintings seem like Misato-chans.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"They are gentle and pretty, and seem to have an inner strength\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(265,297,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Toko-san was that kind of person.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"She seems different from before.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Could it be because shes been busy?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"She seems cold and distant.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I told her about my artwork, and she said to bring that up with people in my class.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I wonder if she was feeling well.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Could it be that Im a bother because Im no longer sick and dont need to see her?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Toko-san is a counselor.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"The sicker I get, the more work she has to do.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Im sorry that I couldnt help with your research report, Toko-san.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Just let me know if you dont want to see me anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(266,298,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I dont want to see her anymore. Im not troubled anymore. To me, Toko-san is\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(267,299,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Mom and Dad have been curt lately.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"My family used to encircle me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"It seems to be coming apart now, since I havent had problems lately.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I wonder if they are busy doing things that they couldnt do while I wasnt well.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I shouldnt complain.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Theyve been so good to me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(268,300,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Doesnt Dad love Mom? Someone tell me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(269,301,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Its been a while since I saw that. Ive become an ordinary kid again.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I have friends; I argue with my parents a little but make up later.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Im in an ordinary family.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Everything is ok, now.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Im an ordinary girl.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(270,302,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Its good to be ordinary.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"People wont look at you funny if youre ordinary.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I dont understand the feelings of people who want to stand out.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I dont have the confidence to want to stand out.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"But is it because Ive become ordinary that Mom and Dad dont pay attention to me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Misato-chan is different.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Shes a friend of ordinary me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(271,303,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Now that I think about it, I havent been checking my e-mails lately.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I quit going to the Net because I saw that, and because of the mean messages people leave there.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Misato-chan said that she goes to the Net, too.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Maybe I should exchange e-mail addresses with her.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"If she knew how active and outgoing I am on the Net, she might be surprised.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"If I had her e-mail address, I wont have to bother calling her by phone.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Moms been complaining because I run up a big phone bill.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Ill talk to Misato-chan tomorrow.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(272,304,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Im surprised at how long I can stay on the phone.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I wonder if Im a very talkative person.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I feel like I can talk and keep on talking to anybody.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(273,305,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Misato-chan turned me down.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"She doesnt like checking e-mails.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"She seems not to have much interest in the Net.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I wonder if she got harassed on the Net, too.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"The way she turned me down was unusual.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Its too bad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I thought she would be happy.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Im a bit sad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Misato-chan will talk to me on the phone, though.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"We can talk to each other anytime, at home or at school.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"She ought to be able to visit the Net on her own.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(274,306,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Im being selfish to want to communicate with Misato-chan over the Net.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(275,307,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"When I checked my computer today, there were about 30 e-mails.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I deleted e-mails if I didnt know who they were from.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"No e-mails from Mr. Rabbit yet.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Didnt my e-mails reach him?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Maybe he hasnt read them yet.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"When I checked the news group, I found that many of the packets had dropped.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Eventually, the members were all people I didnt know.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I got an idea!\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Ill join a news group that has art as a topic.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"There might be people there that are like me, and I can be a lot more outgoing on the Net.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(276,308,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"The Net I full of men.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Arent there any girls?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I dont mind writing guys, but Id rather write girls.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(277,309,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"People talked of nothing but Misato-chans artwork at the cultural fair.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Our senseis prestigious friends came and were very impressed.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Misato-chan is amazing!\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Misato-chan is my best friend.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Isnt that something?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Im so proud.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"But Misato-chan didn\'t look very well.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I wonder if she is ok.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(278,310,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Im somewhat frustrated.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Misato-chan.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Would I feel good if my artwork was praised like hers?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Would I be embarrassed?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I dont know, but Ill probably feel good.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(279,311,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Kazami Sensei mentioned before class that she wants to have Misato-chans artwork presented at the prefectural exhibition.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Its amazing because Misato-chan is still in 7th grade.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Everyone in class went to the cultural fair and saw Misato-chans work.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Even the older kids were really impressed.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Misato-chan doesnt seem too happy, though.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"She seems different lately.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"If shes troubled about something, I wish she would talk to me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(280,312,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I wonder if that is obvious to Misato-chan.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Maybe she doesnt want people to fuss over her.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Will I be disliked if I fuss?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(281,313,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I wonder if people on art sites of the Net are hard to please.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I got friendly and sent pics of Misato-chans artwork, and they said that it was plagiarism.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Misato-chan would never do something like that.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Besides, some artistic big shots saw Misato-chans work and didn\'t think it was plagiarism.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Why then would it be?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I feel contradicted.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I dont want to visit this Net site again.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I feel like I am the one being criticized.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Misato-chan and I have been around each other so much that we can tell whats going on with the other without talking too much.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(282,314,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Does Misato understand me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(283,315,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"They decided not to submit Misato-chans artwork to the prefectural exhibition.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I dont know why.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Sensei didnt explain why.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Misato-chan has stopped talking and looks terrible.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Ive never seen her like this.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"What happened?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Im sad for Misato-chan.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(284,316,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I didnt talk to her at all today.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I hesitated to call.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Could she be waiting for me to call?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"But maybe that isnt true.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(285,317,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Misato-chan skipped school today.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Some of the older kids in art class were spreading rumors.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"They were talking about Misato-chans artwork and plagiarism.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"The kids stopped talking when they noticed that I was listening.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"This makes me feel bad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Misato-chan would never do something like that.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Never.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(286,318,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I cant call Misato-chan.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Im frustrated but cant do anything.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I dont have enough courage.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I cant imagine what Misato-chan would say.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(287,319,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Misato-chan didnt show up at school again today, so I took my notes to her home.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Misato-chans mom came to the door, but Misato-chan didnt.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Is she feeling so bad that she cant even come to the door?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Could it be that she doesnt like me anymore?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"That would make me very sad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"No matter what other kids say about Misato-chan, Ill always be her friend.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I want to see you, Misato-chan.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(288,320,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I just want to see you.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I wont ask you any questions.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I wont ask you about things you dont want to talk about.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(289,321,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I talked to Kasumi sensei today.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I believe in Misato-chan, but I wanted to see what was actually going on.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"The sensei said that there is an art magazine in America with a painting by a Japanese artist very similar to Misato-chans.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I didnt want to see the magazine, but I wanted to make sure.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"The picture in the magazine and Misato-chans painting looked alike.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"They were more than alike.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I could not tell the difference between the two.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"It seems that the Japanese artist who painted it was just a novice, and that it was the first time she won a prize for her artwork.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I searched the Net about it when I got home.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Dad said that that the artwork was by a second-generation Japanese or something.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Misato-chan would never plagiarize.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Still, the paintings looked so similar.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"But I thought that Misato-chan did her work before this other person submitted hers to this magazine.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"Im going to look into it and clear her name.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"Sensei said that people often come up with the same ideas at the same time.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"It was probably a coincidence.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(290,322,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Couldnt it be obvious that people see the same things and have the same ideas about them?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"If the perceived information is the same for two people and they think the same things about it, why would it be odd if those people produce the same impressions about what they see?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Were all human beings, after all.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(291,323,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"The magazine is called Beauty of the Art. It had a homepage, so I sent them an e-mail.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I wonder if Ill hear back from them.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Ill keep writing until I hear back from them.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Im going to get to the bottom of this and Im going to clear Misato-chan of this plagiarism charge.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"But I might see that again when I go to the Net, and that frightens me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(292,324,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Could it be that Im not changing?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"If I think that Im not changing, I wont change.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"But I have changed.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I wont have hallucinations anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(293,325,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I got an e-mail from the editors today.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Im glad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Misato-chans artwork came first.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I saw her sketch over 2 months before the other one was published.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Could this sort of thing happen often?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"The same picture at the same time, both by a Japanese, all by coincidence?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"What is that other artist like?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I couldnt find a home page for her.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I wish I had information about her.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"I know that Misato-chan was right all along, and I feel much better now.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Ill go to Misato-chans home tomorrow.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(294,326,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Misato-chan is going to another school?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Why?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"She didnt say anything to me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"We were friends.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"We were best friends.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"All the other kids said that she went to a different school because she was embarrassed to be found out as a plagiarizer.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"They were saying nasty things.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I cant forgive them for that.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Theyre wrong.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Misato-chan would never plagiarize.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I found out for a fact that she didnt.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Those kids dont know what they are talking about.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"But why did she go away?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"Misato-chan, this is horrible.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"Will I never see you again?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"Its too sad to lose you like this.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"Misato-chan.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(295,327,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Why do people spread rumors without knowing what they are talking about?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Dont they care about who they might be hurting?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(296,328,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Im alone again.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I don\'t want to make friends with anyone other than Misato-chan.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Making friends.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I dont know what strange things these kids think about me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I dont care.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Its all a big nuisance.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"School isnt any fun anyway.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"School without Misato-chan is no fun.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(297,329,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"When will I make friends again? When it happens, will I have to change, too? Even when Im me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(298,330,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I went to Misato-chans home today, but no one was there.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"She must have moved.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"She literally left without saying a word.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"This makes me sad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Didnt she think of me as a friend?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I guess Misato-chan didnt think much of me after all.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I havent received any phone calls or letters.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"If she really was a friend, she would never have left this way.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Maybe she thinks Im badmouthing her like the other kids.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"I makes me even sadder.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I was your special friend.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Wasnt I, Misato-chan?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(299,331,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Would it have been different if I had called you then?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Couldnt you have said that I was on your side?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I was only thinking about you, Misato-chan.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(300,332,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I was thinking of not seeing Toko-san anymore today.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"When I told her about Misato-chan, she said that there are some things that people cant say, even to those who are closest to them.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Did Misato-chan go away because I was hiding things about myself from her?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Is that why she went away without saying anything to me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Even if theres something I cant say, I would never do that.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Toko-san and Misato-chan are awful.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Nobody understands me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I dont feel like doing schoolwork.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Am I a truant?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"I dont want to leave people behind.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Ive got to fight.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Although they say that I ought to study what interests me, the only things Im interested in are Misato-chan and myself.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"But its over.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"I have to find other things that are meaningful to me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(301,333,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Mom and Dad had a big fight today.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Dad never hits people, but he hit Mom today.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Mom threw things at Dad and screamed.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I was afraid and couldnt do anything but cry.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Why did they fight?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"They usually get along so well.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Was it my fault?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(302,334,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Why do people around me become this way?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Is it because Ive become ordinary?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Has it been this way, and I just didnt notice?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(303,335,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Today I told Mom that I wanted to quit counseling.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"She said no.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"She said that Im ok now, but that she doesnt know if I will get worse again.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Ive been missing school again lately.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I didnt want to face it, but Mom is right.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I have to go see Toko-san again tomorrow.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I dont want to.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I have no freedom.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Im a patient.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Im a patient that always has to be looked after.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I dont want to do this anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(304,336,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"What is the meaning of my existence?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(305,337,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Today I think I felt the way a person feels when she wants to die.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I was placed in the same class as Kyoko-chan.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I used to think that I would never feel badly facing Kyoko-chan again, but I became the person I used to be as soon as I saw her.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Kyoko-chan walked past me as if I wasnt there and started talking to other kids.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Im sure she talks about me a lot.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"It cant be helped.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Its true that Im the depressing, strange kid who misses school.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I want to move to another school, too.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I want to disappear.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(306,338,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Ive been going to the library alone to read books.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Its depressing.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"But its better than spending free time at school alone.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I have to distract myself with books.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(307,339,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Mom and Dad had another fight.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"It was about me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I felt so miserable that I couldnt be around it.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I ran away to my room.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Dad got worried and came to check in on me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Dad saw me crying and apologized to me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Why did he apologize?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Arent I the one at fault?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Im the one that should apologize.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Im sorry, Dad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(308,340,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Am I the one at fault? What about me is wrong?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(309,341,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I wonder what I did.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"When I came to, I was on top of the bed.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I thought I went to school as usual.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Did I fall?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"All I remember is walking toward school.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I asked Mom, but she didnt say anything.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I feel like something awful has happened.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"What happened?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I can see hallucinations in my dreams again.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"I hear all sorts of voices.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Im going crazy.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Im not cured after all.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"Theres something wrong with me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"I have to see Toko-san.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(310,342,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I thought I was better.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I wonder what happened.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Why dont I remember anything?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Theres a white mist inside my head.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Everything is mixed with everything else and I cant tell what from what.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(311,343,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Mom said that she went to my school to ask for a leave of absence.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I thought that I ought to feel glad that I wont have to go to school, but Im sad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Ive genuinely been separated from society.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I feel that Ive been rejected by everyone, and Im sad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Can\'t I live an ordinary life anymore?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Dad wont come home and Mom looks worn out.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Why wont Dad come home?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Doesnt he want to see me anymore?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Doesnt Dad like me anymore?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"I want to see him.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I fell asleep weeping, and saw hallucinations again.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Its scary.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"I can see them whether Im asleep or not.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"I cant believe it myself.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"I dont understand it.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"I want someone to prove to me that I am the person that I know I am.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"I want to see Dad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"I want to see Dad and hug him.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"Its ok\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(312,344,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Will everyone I love become unhappy? Will they become unhappy because I feel love for them?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(313,345,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Lately, Ive been taking correspondence courses and surfing the Net day and night.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I start to feel sick looking at the computer screen all day.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Dad bought me this computer, though, so I want to study hard with it.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Mom left the house with the keys so that I cant leave.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Someone help me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I hate being alone.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Ill be a good kid.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Please dont leave me alone.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(314,346,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"My only way to communicate with the outside world is through the Net.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I cant use the phone because I have no one to call, but I can connect with the Net right away.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I can connect with someone that I dont even see.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(315,347,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Even when I go to see Toko-san, Mom drives me now.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Its like shes guarding me, and I hate it.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I can go see Toko-san on my own.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I wonder what Toko-san really thinks of me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I remember talking to her a lot, though I dont remember what we were talking about.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I dont care what Toko-san thinks of me now.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Im crazy anyway, so take down all the weird data you can about me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I dont care anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(316,348,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Am I Moms kid?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Could I be someone elses kid?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"My hair color is different from hers, and her face doesnt look like mine.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(317,349,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I looked for Mr. Rabbit on the Net.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"He was dead.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Weve been out of touch for a long time.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"He had an e-mail address, but he hasnt used it for a year or so.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Maybe he took a break from the Net like I did.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"We discussed things that werent interesting or useful.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"What I want is to find the image of the real me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(318,350,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Is my own physical appearance an illusion or an ordinary phenomenon?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(319,351,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Mom and Dad divorced.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Dad hugged me on the day he left.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I was happy to have him hug me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"He was warm and gentle.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I wont see him for a while.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Im ok with being Dads daughter.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Im the one at fault.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Im the cause.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I hurt Mom and Dad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Im a bad kid.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I dont want Dad to leave.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Will he hug me again?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"Im sure Ill see him again.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(320,352,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Dad\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(321,353,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I share this big house with Mom now.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"The weeds are growing outside because Dad used to pull them, but hes no longer here.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, 