: 8, \"text\": \"Ill need help.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(356,387,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Today the construction was finished and the building was handed over to me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I wonder what he thought about not meeting his client directly at all.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Moreover, since it was a bit of a big effort, I wonder if that made it seem all the more suspicious to him.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I decided to keep an eye on his actions for a while.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"It would be dangerous for Father to be exposed.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(357,388,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Today, I took Dad to his new home.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I took tape media because hard discs are heavy, but decoding them will take time.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I took Dads legs and arms over little by little in the meantime, so I dont think I did so badly.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Luckily, Mom got drunk and fell asleep.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"It will be difficult to visit Dad from now on, though.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(358,389,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I wanted to attach Dads legs, but working on the lower body was difficult.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Its creepy.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I wouldnt mind if Dad only had an upper body.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I cant remove these cables.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Its creepy that Dad doesnt have a head.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I put an empty artificial head on him for the time being.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Hes able to talk, but poorly, and watching the expression on his face as he tries to enunciate seems phony to me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"This isnt Dad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I failed, but what can I do?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(359,390,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Was the only part of Dads body that I cared about his upper body?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Maybe I didnt even acknowledge his body.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"In my mind, Dad was always bigger than me\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(360,391,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Today I walked past a girl I knew in 7th grade, but she didnt seem to notice me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"We hadnt talked much in school, so I didnt mind that she didnt seem to see me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"When I saw her school uniform, I was jealous.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I dont think anyone remembers me anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(361,392,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"My uniform was at the dry cleaners.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Mom seemed sad when she went to the store to pick it up.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"She went to the trouble of buying it for me, after all.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(362,393,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I e-mailed a kid that used to be a classmate, and asked her about me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Isnt the me that acknowledges my existence only living in this small body?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I dont have an individual personality and I dont leave much of an impression.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Nobody remembers me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"When I made Dad, I started to feel that my own body was pretty lame.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Wouldnt I be me if I had a thought re-routing?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I dont need a connection to reality anymore, and its not so important to know that Im a human being who will die unless she eats.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Its more rational to me to have Dad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(363,394,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Dad was having some trouble.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I noticed that he was starting to move around on his own.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Could it be that hes trying to see me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Ill always keep an eye on you, Dad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Im connected to you.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(364,395,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Is Dad really Dad? Is he the Dad that loves me more than anyone else?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(365,396,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Someone has accessed Dad. But who? Some prankster who found my host site?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(366,397,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I had a hallucination for the first time in a long while.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I dont know who I saw.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"The me in the hallucination has grown.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"She is in elementary school.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"But shes different from the person I was then.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"She had conviction in her eyes.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Was the me that I was then me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"This is no good.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I cant handle this on my own.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Ill go see Toko-san.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(367,398,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Maybe Toko-san doesnt understand me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"She asks, Are you really Lain? She just tilts her head when I bring up my medical condition.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I dont know why Im going to see her.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"She seems frightened of me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Toko-san, it seems that you are beginning to not understand me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I havent been changing.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(368,399,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Even a me like that cant remember what I talked about.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I felt bad for Toko-san and wanted to help her.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"And then\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(369,400,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I was concerned, so I accessed Toko-sans notebook.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I found data about me that I wasnt able to see before.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I went ahead and downloaded and saved the information.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"These days I get unusually tired and see hallucinations.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"It drives me crazy.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Im getting drowsy again although I was sleeping just a moment ago.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I have a lot of e-mails.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I dont even want to look at them.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Im sleepy.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"But if I sleep again, I might see myself again.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I hate this.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Dad\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(370,401,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"In the mail there was a letter from Mr. Rabbit.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"It was bright and gentle, like he was before he went away.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I wanted to say, Hey, its been a long time! and write him, but I couldnt.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(371,402,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Whats wrong with me? Im like the me I used to be. Who am I?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(372,403,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"How did she find my e-mail address?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Misato-chans mail came to my private, hidden site.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"She wrote in a familiar tone as if we were still great friends.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Misato-chan and Mr. Rabbit both seem to do as they please.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I was waiting to hear from them for such a long time.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I wrote down their phone numbers quickly and sent them e-mails.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Im still waiting to hear from them.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Have they turned their backs on me again?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(373,404,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"A bug was found in the mail?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"The dates and times of the e-mails are fabricated.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Could it be a problem with the server?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Ill have to contact the server.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(374,405,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Mom isnt at home.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Where did she go?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Did she run away?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Could she be drunk out on the street somewhere?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I called the police and asked them to investigate.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"They didnt believe me because Im a kid, but they came to my house to check.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I want to tell Dad, but I have no way of contacting him.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Only Mom knows where he is.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"A young police officer was badmouthing.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"He said that Mom must have evaporated. Mom isn\'t that kind of person.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I felt bitter and couldnt stop crying.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"I was so mad I absolutely messed up the police host site.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"How do you jerks like that?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"I protect people who are important to me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(375,406,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Ive been getting weird phone calls.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I pick up the receiver and hear dead silence.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Either that, or I get creepy weirdo phone calls.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I thought of stopping the phone, but Mom and Dad and Misato-chan wont be able to contact me then.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I answered the phone as much as I could, but I got tired, so I pulled out the plug before going to bed.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"When I wake up, I am afraid of hearing Die, weirdo! screamed from myself.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(376,407,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Someone is trying to irritate me. Why? Why would someone do that to me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(377,408,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"When I awoke I was grasping a gun.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"The smell of death and metal woke me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I dont understand it anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Im absolutely crazy.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I got scared.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I took the gun, put it in a shopping bag, and hid it in a desk drawer.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Theres a key to the drawer, but it isnt any good.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I know.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Ill hide it inside of Dad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(378,409,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Mom is missing and Dad cant be contacted.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Im alone.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"When I went to see Dad robot he hugged me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"But thats funny.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"How did he know that it was me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Did he hear me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Could he tell by the sound of my footsteps?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I didnt think he could do that.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Something might be wrong with Dads development.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"At first I was happy and didnt mind, but at this specification, there is something wrong with his speed.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I wonder why.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Is there a reason I dont know about?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(379,410,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"One of my neighbors is starting rumors.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Why is she trying to tell me about it?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"She laughs when I turn around.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"What does she want to do to me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(380,411,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I decided to make a copy of myself and put it on the Net.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I replicated my voice and appearance in detail.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"For thought routing, I rebuilt a system similar to Dads, enhanced it, and dispersed it over the Net.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"This way, as long as there is a Net, Im a person who will never die.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Just like Dad.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(381,412,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Its almost a consolation.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I know that what Im doing is meaningless.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Im wondering if the me in the Net will evolve in a strange way.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(382,413,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I spend over half of each day in a nightmare.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Maybe the world of nightmares is reality and whats called reality is a dream.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Maybe theyre intermeshed.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"After all, I have hallucinations when Im sleeping and I have them when Im awake.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Im starting not to know which is which.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"That girl become a junior high school student.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Her height is the same as mine.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Its like Im looking in the mirror.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"But I dont think anyone will see this girl.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"She couldnt be seen up till now.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Theres nothing to be concerned about.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(383,414,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I talked to the me on the Net.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Shes the same as me, so shes predictable.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Because Im me, I can imagine how Im going to be.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I played with the me on the Net, deliberately making her angry and making her laugh.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Did she think I was fun, too?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(384,415,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"When I told Toko-san about Mom, she looked at me with a blank expression on her face.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Theres something the matter with Toko-san.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Shes hiding something.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(385,416,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Who? Mom and Dad are together? Toko-san, you know about my parents, dont you? Who was with them?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(386,417,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I killed Dad today. Mom is next.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(387,418,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Its been a year, Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Lain, it feels good to get back to a diary after a long time, doesnt it?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"This is my count down.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(388,419,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Lain, what do you want?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Pleasure?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Excitement?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Friends?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"What I need right now is someone who wants to know me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Toko-san promised me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"She said that she would understand me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"She said that she would choose me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(389,420,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I took my last walk.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"As I walked around town all day, I noticed Mom.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"She didnt notice me at all.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"She looked at me like a total stranger.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I cant forgive her for that.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I dont have to worry about her anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(390,421,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"From the standpoint of many religions, wont I go to hell?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Who will pass judgment on the me on the Net?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"How about me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Will God pass judgment on me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"At any rate, I dont need my body anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(391,422,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"You people who want to know me, why do you want to know me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Will you benefit from knowing me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Am I for your research?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"For a stupid TV show?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(392,423,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Do I have a sad existence?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I guess people think so.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I dont mind that much.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I dont need a backup.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"That would be useless.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"The me on the Net also had a sad existence.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Thats why I killed her.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Hey, did that hurt?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(393,424,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Even when Im not dying, my body feels fear.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Mysterious.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Is the reason that I have the potential to feel fear no matter what I do because of whats recorded in my genes?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I dont need those kind of genes.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"This is a small world that seems large only to parasites.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(394,425,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Do you know where Im going?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I dont know either.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Thats because Im going to be born soon.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Will I become a more evolved human being?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"If I think so I might as well think so.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"A human without a body isnt human?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"There are people who have bodies that arent human.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Is that me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Im not human?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Lain is Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"What is it to be human?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Youre human if you have a body?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"Im me.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"Am I just conglomerated with my body?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"I need a body if Im going to live in the real world.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"Suicide would be stupid.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"It would be better to just die naturally.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"I dont need it.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"I might need it someday.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"That might be true.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"I wont need a body to live in the Wired.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 21, \"text\": \"Ill need the recollections of the body.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 22, \"text\": \"How about the recollections of a body that grows older?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 23, \"text\": \"My point of view may change?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 24, \"text\": \"Is there a need for it to change?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 25, \"text\": \"Theres no guarantee that that will be you.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 26, \"text\": \"Lain, what do I need to be on the Wired?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 27, \"text\": \"Existence and will.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 28, \"text\": \"The rest is just data.\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(395,426,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"When this summer vacation is over Ill graduate.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Im a bit happy and a bit sad.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Takeshi-san will be returning to Japan one step ahead of me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I guess that cant be helped.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Hes a brilliant guy.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"The people at the sponsoring research center wants to give him a new project as soon as possible.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Ahh, shucks!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Im just jealous of him.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I would love to start my own research soon.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Mmm.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"But I have to graduate first.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Its too bad though, because I wanted to be with Takeshi-san until the graduation ceremony.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(396,427,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Today was so cool that I couldnt believe that it was mid-summer.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I suppose its sticky and uncomfortable in Japan right now.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"But why am I thinking about Japan all of a sudden?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(397,428,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"There will be a party at a friends home tomorrow, so I made an apple pie.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"When I gave Takeshi-san a slice, he said that with a pie as sweet as the one I made, everyone aside from himself at the party would enjoy it.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"He said that my baking had become Americanized.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Its true that compared to the cakes and pies in America, Japanese desserts are usually much less sweet.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"At first I didnt bake things this sweet.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"But now, I feel that unless I make my desserts sweet, they would be unsatisfactory.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"If I get used to all this sweet stuff, I wont want to eat pastries when I return to Japan.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"If I dont cool it I could get fat and Takeshi-san wont like me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Ill have to start another diet tomorrow!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Hee, hee.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(398,429,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Hmm.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Its almost Halloween again.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Itll be my last Halloween here.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Halloween surprised me at first.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"People would walk around in costumes day and night, having lunch and shopping as if everything was as usual.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"People would come out in frightening costumes at night.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I used to go out in a costume with my college friends too.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I think Takeshi-san isnt into that kind of thing.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Ive never seen him in a costume.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"It would be fun if we could go out in costumes together.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I wonder what kind of costume Ill wear this year.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"When I see Jack-o-lanterns on Halloween night, I sometimes wish I could just stay here and live with Takeshi-san.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"Hee, hee.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(399,430,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Today I took a walk with Takeshi-san along the Charles River.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I reflected on the four years that Ive spent here.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"At first I was elated, but things were tough until I met Takeshi-san.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I think Ive changed a lot since I met him.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I suppose it wasnt time for romance, but being alone was a downer.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"When you feel down you want someone to be around you.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Bu it doesnt mean that you ought to seek out a boyfriend thoughtlessly just because youre feeling sad.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Ive gotten my feelings hurt a few times that way.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"But Takeshi-san is different.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"I feel safe just being with him.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I think its the first time Ive felt this way.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Next year Takeshi-san will return to Japan and enter a research center there.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"What will happen to me?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"I would love to work in the same research center as Takeshi-san.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(400,431,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"The year is nearly over.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Takeshi-san will return to Japan early next year.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I wont go back until I graduate, so I wont see him for 3 months.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I havent been away from him for a long time, so I feel a tad worried.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I wonder if he is ok.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"But the good news is that Ill work with him at the same research center in Japan next year.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Im going to try to enjoy the rest of my time here as a student.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"At the end of year there will be New Years Eve, and plenty of fun events taking place!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(401,432,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Hmmm.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Next month.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Takeshi-san will return to Japan then.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"He said that hell celebrate my birthday with me because it will be before he leaves.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"But knowing that he will leave bums me out.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"When I go to the airport, Ill want to cry.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(402,433,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Takeshi-san went home to Japan today.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I didnt know what to talk about on the way to the airport.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I was looking for words.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Did I make him feel uncomfortable?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"But Takeshi-san is a gentle guy.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"He didnt say anything.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"He just held my hand.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"He said that hell be waiting for me in Japan.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Thats right.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Ill see him again soon.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(403,434,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I got a letter from Takeshi-san.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"He said, Lets celebrate your graduation when you return to Japan. Im so happy!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Takeshi-san is working hard at his research center.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Ive been sad about him being away for a long time now, but thats embarrassing.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Takeshi-san is working so hard.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I have to work hard, too.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I have to work hard and do research, and become a good researcher that others will be impressed by.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I want to go home to Japan soon.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Takeshi-san will be waiting for me there.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(404,435,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Today I cleaned my room to prepare leaving for Japan.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I have so many memories and photos.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Theyre all treasures to me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I cant take everything with me, though, so I talked to Mary about selling them in a flea market.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Mary seemed a bit sad, too.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Dont worry, Mary.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Im going to give everything my best in Japan.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(405,436,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Im home!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Im back in Japan after 5 years.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Hee, hee.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Japan is great.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Living in America was good, but I feel at ease being back home.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Im a tad scared, though.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"When you come home after being away for so long, you start to feel singled out.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I remember being insecure in junior high school, too.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I would be tardy for school and Mom scolded me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Five years sure went fast.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I had no time to be homesick.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"But you worked really hard, didn\'t you, Toko?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"Study, study, study.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"But I made good friends and there were good times and bad times too.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"I had romance that didnt work out, but I had romance that worked out, too.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"Looking back, I wonder what about me improved the most.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"Hee, hee.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"Im ok, Im ok!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"Have self-confidence and fight, Toko!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"I start working at the research center tomorrow.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"I want to end all my worries to end today.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 21, \"text\": \"When I go to the research center tomorrow, I might see Takeshi-san.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(406,437,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Welcome home, Touko.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Im so tired today.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I dont like the air in Japanese research centers.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Why do Japanese research centers have this sort of feel?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"The people entirely lack a critical mentality, and they are lazy.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"They give you a prejudicial glare when you mention that you just returned from studying abroad.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I wish they would cut it out.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Research centers in America werent like this.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I suppose they think I was able to study abroad because my dad has connections.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Everybody is so icy here.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"When I was in grade school, we were so welcoming of kids transferring from other schools.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Maybe we change when we grow up.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"This makes me depressed, but its what I have to face now.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"I cant live like I did in America forever.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"If I do what Im supposed to do, people will give me credit eventually.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"Ok, Touko?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"Soon Ill have my examination to become a counselor.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"Until I finish that exam, Ill have to bear with things the best I can.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}]'),(407,438,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"You cant be sluggish, Toko.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I have to work hard and get moving at a good speed.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Everyone is indifferent about me anyway.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I dont care if I dont become super-prestigious.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I want to do the kind of work that I can be proud of.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"That way, good results are sure to follow.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Takeshi-san will be with me, too, so I have nothing to worry about.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Its too bad that Takeshi-sans research center is in a different building, but next week Ill have a date with him!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Im going to purr around him.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(408,439,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Ha, ha.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Today I was able to spend the entire day with Takeshi-san like I havent for the longest time.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Im so happy.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I really, really like him.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Takeshi-sans research center has its own share of cliques and rivalry and it must be hard for him, but he just stayed quiet and listened to me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"When I see his big smile that seems to surround me completely, I feel so much better.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Im so simple-minded.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Im the one who does the purring, though.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Sometimes I want Takeshi-san to purr around me, too.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Even if he wants to, maybe he cant depend on me for that right now.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Im going to work hard so that I can become Takeshi-sans exclusive counselor!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Hee, hee.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(409,440,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Ive felt poorly all day today.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Why do the Japanese like to spread rumors?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I was surprised to learn that people know Im going out with Takeshi-san.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I wish they would stop whispering behind my back.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"For my coworkers to hear things and imagine what might be happening is one thing, but to spread concocted stories about me like they are facts is sickening.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"They say, Oh, those two must be having a lot of fun in bed, or she must be tired of having sex with foreigners. You dont have to talk like that just because youre in the restroom.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Most of those people spreading rumors are probably from the 2nd floor.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"What stupid talk.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Im sure it makes them happy, though.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Ahhhh!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"It makes me so mad!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Now I know why everybody looks at me funny.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"If you want to know about my business, face me and ask me about it.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"But instead you talk about this stuff for everyone to hear.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"Why the hell are you working in a medical research center?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"Do what youre here to do.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"Takeshi-san told me not to mind it.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"I cant forgive these people, though.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"Agh!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"I feel like wringing their necks!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"What gives?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 21, \"text\": \"I cant stay angry at these people forever.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 22, \"text\": \"But I feel rotten today.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 23, \"text\": \"I wish Takeshi-san were here right now.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 24, \"text\": \"But I suppose it would just be a nuisance if I go to him with all this.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 25, \"text\": \"I know hes very busy now.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 26, \"text\": \"I wonder if he knows that all these rumors going around.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 27, \"text\": \"Maybe hes feeling lousy, too.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(410,441,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Agh!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"At a time like this I want to have a drink and forget about everything!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I have a big test coming up and I cant get tied up with all this stuff.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I cant let those jerks get to me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Ill talk with Takeshi-san about this after the tests.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Until then Ill just have to bear with this.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Good night, Takeshi-san.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(411,442,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I received a phone call from Harumi today.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I dont hear from her often.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I was surprised to hear from her.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Shes a bit lazy about making phone calls.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"But I was really surprised when Harumi told me that she was getting married.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"She always used to say how she just broke up with a guy and felt like she just wanted to die, or that she wanted to have a guy introduced to her.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"She calls so infrequently.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I was wondering why she called, and it was about marriage.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I felt sort of relieved and slightly shocked.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"But when a woman is 26 years old, its not odd for her to be married or to have children.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Ohh!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Now Im feeling jealous.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"Thats ok.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"When I go to the wedding, Ill introduce Takeshi-san and make her jealous.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"Maybe Ill get married soon, too.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"I\'ll call Takeshi-san tomorrow.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(412,443,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Today I met with Kanako, one of my naughty friends from college.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Good going, Toko!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I thought of taking her to Harumis wedding, but she said that she might not be able to because she is busy with work.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"How unfeeling!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I havent seen Kanako since I left for America, so I really wanted to get together with her.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Kanako asked if my birthday will be coming up soon.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Shes right.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"They say that things go fast for a woman once shes past twenty years old.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"How true.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Im already 27.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Harumi will get married in September.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"I wonder what Takeshi-san is thinking.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"What will I do for my birthday this year?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"Ahh!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"Maybe I will propose to him!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"But then again, no.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(413,444,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Takeshi-san!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I just passed my test to become a counselor.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Im so relieved.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Its stupid that I have to pass a second test in Japan.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Still, I wanted to let everybody know that I passed.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I wrote Takeshi-san an e-mail all about it.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I wonder if he is happy for me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I wonder if he will call me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I sure wish he would.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(414,445,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I wonder if some of those nasty prejudicial rumors will stop now.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Silly me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"It isnt that Ive been trying to change peoples point of view.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Why should I be worried?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Anyway, I can start my research now.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I have to try really hard starting now.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(415,446,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Hmm.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"As always, a research room is a strenuous place to be.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Even though Ive passed the test, Im treated like I don\'t qualify as a counselor.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I dont care for Professor Takashima.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"He wont send clients my way.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"He leaves me with a lot of menial tasks instead.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"He probably says to himself, the girl who went to America cant do anything. That makes me really frustrated, Takeshi-san.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"If I were a man, I would get recognition sooner.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"My study abroad doesnt seem to count for much.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Its no time to be worked up about Professor Takashimas little chores.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I will get recognized.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(416,447,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Ive been here 6 months, and Professor Takashima still wont send clients my way.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"He gives me this nonsense about how there arent any clients that would be a good fit for me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Such lies.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"He just wants to use me for petty tasks.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I didnt come here to be his secretary.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I hate this.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Ahh!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I dont like that middle-aged old man!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(417,448,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"For the upcoming Golden Week Ill be able to take a few days away from work.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I havent had much rest since I returned from America.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Im happy about the break.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Ive been stressed so much since I started working in the laboratory.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Id like to spend the time with Takeshi-san.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I don\'t need to go traveling with him.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I just want to be around him.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I want some comfort.\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Am I being selfish?\", \"actor\": \"Touko\"}]'),(418,449,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Today I met my first client.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"She is a 12 year old girl named Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I was uneasy at first because I didnt understand why Professor Takashima assigned me someone so young.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"But as soon as I saw Lains face, I felt at ease.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I suppose it was because she was cute.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Hmm.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I had an unusual feeling around her.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Anyhow, even if she is very young, she is my client.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"It seems that she is troubled by auditory and visual hallucinations and feels psychologically unstable.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Could she be having trouble at home?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Could she be forming an image of herself from experiences in early childhood?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"I hope I can help her.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"I hope she will open up to me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"Ill try my best.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(419,450,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Yaay!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Tomorrow Ill have my first date with Takeshi-san since I came back from America.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Im so excited.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I wonder what to wear.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I better not wear anything too flashy, or there will be more rumors about me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I havent bought many clothes lately.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"It\'s hard to go buy clothes at this time of day.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I cant go buy clothes during my date.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I cant do that in front of Takeshi-san.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"I dont want him to get a bad impression about me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(420,451,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I had dinner with Takeshi-san today.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Because we hadnt seen each other for such a long time, I had a lot to talk about.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I talked so much that Takeshi-san was surprised.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Takeshi-san couldnt get off work during Golden Week, so we couldn\'t see each other then.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I thought I would be a little sulky, but once I saw Takeshi-sans face, I lightened up.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"He laughed and listened to all my stories.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"He even gave me flowers to congratulate me for passing my examination.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Its so true that women love to receive flowers!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I want this happiness to last forever.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(421,452,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Oh, I feel so good.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Getting together with him after all this time.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I think Im getting a bit lewd.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"But I think its ok to feel this way.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I really feel loved.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"It feels more natural than it felt when I was in America with him.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"If I get married to him, I want to feel just like this.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(422,453,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I met Lain for the second time today.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"She looked right at me and called me sensei. That made me feel good, and I blushed.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I wonder if Ive become transparent to her already.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I must be an inexperienced counselor if I blush just because Im called a sensei.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"From the first time I met Lain, I had an unusual sense about her.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I wonder what that was.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"When I look at her eyes, I feel as though she can see right through me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I wonder if she feels that I am someone that can help her.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I dont remember myself being as relaxed as Lain when I was her age.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"She seems very composed.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"A 12-year-old is still a child, but Lain seems like an adult.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"They say that kids are all getting precocious these days.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"I guess times are changing.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"Ah!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"Now Im talking like an old woman.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"Dont let any hallucinations beat you, Lain!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"Im going to make you well.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(423,454,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Today was very busy.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I was able to have lunch with Takeshi-san, though.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"He didnt look well today.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"He seemed fidgety and said that he didnt have much time.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I wonder if hes very busy in the research room where he works.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Could it be that he doesnt like me anymore?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"That couldnt be it, could it?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"He said that he cant go to Harumis wedding with me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I wanted to show him off to Harumi so much.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Its too bad.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I wonder if he is being cautious with me because I have wishful thinking about marriage.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Ive heard that that sort of thing can happen.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"But I wanted to at least have a relaxed lunch with him.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"If hes busy though, theres nothing I can do.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"You just have to hang in there, Toko.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"I dont want to be thought of as a selfish person, either.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"But if Takeshi-san no longer likes me, I dont think I could continue living.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"Well, thats not completely true.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"Its too bad that I cant see him for two more weeks.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"Proceed carefully, Toko.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(424,455,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Argh!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I havent written in my diary for days.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Im not entirely slothful about it, but whats the point of keeping a diary if I dont write in it everyday?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Things should be easier for me this week because Professor Takashima will be away.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I want to go do some shopping!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I need to buy a present for Harumi, too.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I wonder if Takeshi-san will go with me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Hell wont mind doing a little shopping with me, will he?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(425,456,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I became emotional at Harumis wedding.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Ive never seen her look so pretty.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"She said she was going on her honeymoon to have a baby right away.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Im glad that she seemed so happy.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I love to see wedding dresses.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Weddings in churches are so romantic.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"There were over 100 invited people attending the reception.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Ive never been to such a large wedding crowd.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Oh, when will I be as happy as Harumi?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"It was unfortunate that although there were many people at the wedding who knew each other, there werent many people for me to talk to.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"And Takeshi-san couldnt come.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Kanoko couldnt, either.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"I know that people living in a society like this have a lot of things they have to do, but I feel that they should make time to go to their friends wedding.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"Ah, well.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"I shouldnt complain.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"Id want all my friends to attend my wedding.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"I guess I really do want to get married.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(426,457,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Today I met with Kanako for the first time in 5 years.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"She didnt seem different at all.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Shes quite a career woman.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"But she does seem a bit relaxed compared to 5 years ago.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Let me leave it at that.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"On the other hand, Kanako said that Ive changed a lot.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"She said that I used to be difficult to approach, but that I seem gentler now.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Is that really true?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"So she used to think that I was difficult and cold?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Grrr!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Shell have no forgiveness from me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(427,458,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Kanako said that she though the freedom and liberation of American living had rubbed off on me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I was a bit embarrassed to hear that.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Looking at the postcard photo from Harumis honeymoon, I laughed.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Im jealous, though I pretend not to be.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Kanako said that she still has no plans of getting married.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I hope that she doesnt proclaim all of a sudden that she will get married, like Harumi did.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"What will I do when Kanako gets married?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Ill be too sad.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Takeshi-san, whats going on with you?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(428,459,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Oh, Im so sick of all this work!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I really dislike Professor Takashima.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"There are other researchers he could delegate to.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Ive been irritable lately.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I havent been able to see Takeshi-san, there have been no new extensions of counseling work, and Ive been doing menial chores.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"All these things are putting me on edge.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Nothing seems to be going well.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Its no good if I become cranky.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Im a counselor.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Im sorry, Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I have to think of my work outside of counseling as part of my work, too.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"I have to do what I have to do and have it recognized.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"Otherwise, Ill fail.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"Now that I think of it, Halloween will be coming soon.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"Back in America, people preparing for Halloween made everyday feel like a festival.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"Those were good days.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"I guess there wont be Halloween or Christmas either this year.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(429,460,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Why do I have to do all these chores?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"This has nothing to do with the Labor Standards Act.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Am I being bullied?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Is my Japanese strange because Im drunk?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Stupid!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Stupid!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Stupid!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Damn it!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"bald-headed Takashima bastard with the blinding shiny bald head!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(430,461,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I wonder how many times Ive met with Lain up till now.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"It seems that she sometimes has hallucinations, but they dont seem to be developing further.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I think that seeing hallucinations must be a very difficult thing for her.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Shes not the kind of child that should have a gloomy personality.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I wonder if she is getting a hard time at school.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Her mother told me that she isnt being bullied.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"When I mention school, Lain tends to become quiet.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Maybe I should ask some of her friends at school how shes doing.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I think the kind of bullying that happens in schools now is different from the kind that took place when I was younger.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"I wish I could help you, Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I feel depressed when I see Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"It cant be helped when I get depressed, but its just at those times that Professor Takashima complains to me about trifling matters.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"Ahh!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"Tomorrow I have the day off.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"Ill go on the town and relax.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(431,462,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Lately, Takeshi-san has been acting strangely.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"When I call, he always says that hes busy.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I understand if hes busy with work, but I wish he werent so cold with me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"And why did he decide not to see me on my birthday?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Id hate to say, is your work more important than me? but Im starting to want to say it.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Im 27 years old, Takeshi-san.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"You were very happy with me when I passed my examination.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Lately I dont even see you at the research lab.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"It worries me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"I hope its all my imagination.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Things seem to be getting gloomy for me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Things havent been going very well.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"Im going to bed.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"The more I think about this stuff, the more uneasy I get.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(432,463,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Lain gave me a present.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"It was a combination present for my birthday and for Valentines Day coming up.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"She gave me cookies to go with my tea.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"She said that she made the cookies with her mother because she knew that I like something with my tea.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I was very moved by her.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"What are you doing getting so moved by a client, Toko?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Maybe its because Takeshi-san didnt give me a birthday present.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"That was terrible of you, Takeshi-san.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Lately Ive been moody.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"I suddenly become sad or depressed.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Is it because Im getting older?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"But how did Lain know my birthday?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"Did I tell her?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"I dont suppose it matters.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"Its the first time Ive received a gift from a girl, though.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"Its a bit embarrassing.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"Thank you, Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(433,464,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"It will soon be Valentines Day.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"It seems like a Japanese celebration.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"It makes me think.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Takeshi-san didnt even meet me on my birthday.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I just received a flower delivery a week afterwards.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"There were no phone calls.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I think he really doesnt like me anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I just keep feeling let down.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Here I am with some chocolate.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"How dumb can it all get?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"But this is the end.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Whats the use?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"I give up.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"Tomorrow, Ill place it in Takeshi-sans desk drawer.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(434,465,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I got a phone call from Takeshi-san today!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Thanks for the chocolates, he said!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Im sorry that I was busy and didnt call you back for so long, he said!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I had been so worried and worked up.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Im a pretty simple person.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Im so glad.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"He doesnt dislike me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"He really was just very busy.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(435,466,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Its ok for me to believe in it.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(436,467,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I got an e-mail from Harumi.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"It was all about her honeymoon, and it seemed like she didnt care what was going on with me at all.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Thats fine.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"But since youre happy, cant you involve me in your discussion a little?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Well.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Aside from Takeshi-san, Harumi and Kanako are the only people I confide in.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Maybe I need more friends, but I dont have the personality to warm up to everyone.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"These are all my own personal problems, after all.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Its not time to be taking care of other people.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"I think Ill talk to Professor Takashima tomorrow and ask him to let me stop counseling Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"But if I do that, I really will have nothing to do.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"If all I do here is petty chores, I might as well quit being here.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(437,468,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"A resignation.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Ive never resigned from anything in my life.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"This is hard for me.\", \"actor\": 