ied about Takeshi-san, I will also feel unstable.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"This isnt good.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"As a counselor, I shouldnt feel this way.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I have to fix myself before I try to fix Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(441,472,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Oh, what a surprise!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"To run into Yoshida-kun at a place like that.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I thought that it was weird for a guy to be buying underwear alone.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Maybe he was shopping for his girlfriend.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I feel embarrassed.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"It was nice to talk to him, though, and I have nothing to worry about.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I guess Ive been stressed lately.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I sure ran my mouth with Yoshida-kun.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I think I bothered him.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Well, theres no sense in regretting it now.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Yoshida-kun does seem very grown up for his age.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"He surprised me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"Hes not as grown up as Takeshi-san, though.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"He said, Toko-san, you seem tired. He was gentle, and I was a bit touched.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"No, no, Toko.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"Yoshida-kun was just feeling sorry for you.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"Ohh.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"Maybe his girlfriend saw him talking to me and got angry at him.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"He seems so cheerful at the lab.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 19, \"text\": \"He said that hell bring some sample medical utensils next time he swings by.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 20, \"text\": \"Ill get over my stress soon.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(442,473,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Oh!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Just when I thought I was able to meet Yoshida-kun, I screwed it up!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"He said that he was waiting at the department store, talking to the person in charge of health equipment.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Oh, Im such a careless person.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"He suddenly apologized to me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Yoshida-kun was probably angry.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Ahh.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Ive done something embarrassing again.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"He was just bringing the health equipment he promised to bring.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"The machine he brought was like a toy.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Its used for relaxation.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"I wonder if it works.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"Its supposed to work best if you use it everyday.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"I think Ill start using it tonight.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"I bet Yoshida-kun gets girlfriends easily.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"Hes such a good-looking guy and hes tall.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 16, \"text\": \"When he comes to the lab, all the women seem to really take notice of him.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 17, \"text\": \"Oh, what am I thinking?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 18, \"text\": \"