ko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"My heart beat so fast!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I wondered if he would pretend that he wasnt married to someone else.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I suddenly froze; I couldnt move my body or my face.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Takeshi-san smiled and just said, Hey, you look really good. Is that all?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Is that all you have to say to me?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"The next moment, I found myself starting to laugh.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Takeshi-san was surprised and ran away.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"I wonder why.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"Why did I laugh?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Did Takeshi-san think that I went crazy?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"Is there really something wrong with my mind?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"Could this all be a dream?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"Sometimes I cant tell whats real or whats a dream.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"Someonehelp me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(461,492,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Ill stop using the RML today.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I think I lost confidence in myself because I depended on this device.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I am me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Lain is an ordinary girl.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Takeshi-san is an ordinary man who found someone he likes more than me and married her, but was too weak-willed to tell me about it.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I dont like Takeshi-san anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(462,493,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I had dinner with Yoshida-kun today.\", \"acto