 \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"I asked her, Who are you?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Are you really Lain? Without changing her expression but looking upward, she said, Im me. A question with such an obvious answer.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Still, before even thinking about it, my mouth was open.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"I wonder why.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"I think Lain is probably tired of it, too.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \"I know.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \"It has to do with the girl Ive been seeing in my dreams lately who looks a lot like Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"She looks like Lain, but she isnt her.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 14, \"text\": \"I better straighten my mind out.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 15, \"text\": \"Otherwise I wont be much of a counselor.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(465,496,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I went to the cemetery to pay respect to Professor Takashima with the other employees.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Its been a year already since he died.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"So many things have happened this last year.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Rest in peace.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(466,497,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"I understand myself less and less day by day.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I was seeing strange dreams, but up till now I thought it was just because I was mentally confused.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"But today, I had an auditory hallucination.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Im not positive that it was a hallucination, but since yesterday, my ears havent stopped ringing.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Its as if Im Lain.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Orgel?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"What is it?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Its as if something is ringing inside my head.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Tomorrow Ill go see a doctor that specializes in hearing.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(467,498,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"When I was organizing the data I have about Lain, I started to hear the voices of researchers although there was no one there.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I couldnt tell what they were saying.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Im sure it was gossip about me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I thought I heard Yoshida-kuns voice, too.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Why did I hear him?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Whats wrong?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"Whats happening to me?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"Someone tell me!\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Someone help me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \"I cant organize data when Im like this.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"Ill do it tomorrow.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(468,499,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Tomorrow?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Will tomorrow be ok?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Am I going crazy?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"If Im crazy, no one would want to be around me, would they?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"Who can I turn to for help?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I cant believe anyone.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"HelpYoshida-kun.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(469,500,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Toko: I stopped using RML.\", \"actor\": \"\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I dont know why, but I felt I had to.\", \"actor\": \"\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Yoshida-kun, Im sorry.\", \"actor\": \"\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"I sometimes worry that you stay with me because it has to do with your work.\", \"actor\": \"\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I want to see Yoshida-kun.\", \"actor\": \"\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I want to see him and kiss him.\", \"actor\": \"\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"He knows that I feel this way.\", \"actor\": \"\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I want him to embrace me.\", \"actor\": \"\"}]'),(470,501,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"When I was organizing data again today, I had a sensation like the one I experienced while working with RML.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"I experienced bright white flashes of light pulsing through my head.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"I thought it was dangerous.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"It wasnt as if I used the equipment incorrectly.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I might have been mistaken to use it in the first place.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"Was it manufactured improperly?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"This is dangerous.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \"I have to tell Yoshida-kun.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"Selling this machine is dangerous.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(471,502,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Thats itif things continue this way, Lain will control me completely.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"Lain must have seen all of the data here.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \"Why did she?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"Why is all of Lains life history stored here?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"I dont understand anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"I can hear the voices again.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": 