body is over there anymore.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(657,688,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Dont think that Im trying to fool you. Im not trying to fool anyone.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(658,689,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Good night. Ill be waiting for you tomorrow.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(659,690,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Say, what were you doing? It looked like fun.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(660,691,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Go ahead and laugh.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(661,692,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Even if were together, were too far away.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(662,693,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Are you the one that wakes me up?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(663,694,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Your special power woke me.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(664,695,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Thats why its my turn to wake you up next time.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(665,696,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Close your eyes and listen. Can you tell that Im nearby? Can you hear my footsteps?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(666,697,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"My voice. Can you hear it?\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(667,698,'en','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Im trying to touch you now.\", \"actor\": \"Toko\"}]'),(677,247,'ru','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \"Are the people who enjoy doing horrible things and hurting people really human beings like me?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"But what am I?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}]'),(678,11,'ru','[{\"line\": 0, \"text\": \" ,       .\", \"actor\": \"Girl\"}, {\"line\": 1, \"text\": \"?\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 2, \"text\": \", !\", \"actor\": \"Girl2\"}, {\"line\": 3, \"text\": \"     .\", \"actor\": \"Girl2\"}, {\"line\": 4, \"text\": \"       ...     100%  .\", \"actor\": \"Girl2\"}, {\"line\": 5, \"text\": \"  .\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 6, \"text\": \"! !\", \"actor\": \"Girl\"}, {\"line\": 7, \"text\": \",   ,   ?\", \"actor\": \"Girl2\"}, {\"line\": 8, \"text\": \"   ?\", \"actor\": \"Girl2\"}, {\"line\": 9, \"text\": \" .\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 10, \"text\": \"   .\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 11, \"text\": \".\", \"actor\": \"Lain\"}, {\"line\": 12, \"text\": \" ,    ...\", \"actor\": \"Girl\"}, {\"line\": 13, \"text\": \"...\", \"actor\": \"Girl2\"}]');
